\id JHN - Biblica® Open New Luo Translation 2020 
\h Johana 
\toc1 Injili Mar Johana 
\toc2 Johana 
\toc3 Joh 
\mt2 Injili Mar 
\mt1 Johana 
\c 1  
\s1 Wach nodoko dhano 
\p  
\v 1 Kar chakruok, Wach ne nitie, kendo Wach ne ni kod Nyasaye, kendo Wach ne en Nyasaye.  
\v 2 Ne en gi Nyasaye nyaka aa chakruok.  
\v 3 En ema nomiyo gik moko duto ochwe; kendo ka dine onge en, to onge gima dine ochwe mosechwe.  
\v 4 Ngima ne ni kuome, kendo ngimano ne en ler ni ji.  
\v 5 Lerno rieny ei mudho, to mudho pok oime. 
\p  
\v 6 Nyasaye nooro ngʼat moro ma nyinge Johana.  
\v 7 Nobiro kaka janeno mondo otim nend lerno, mondo kanyalore to ji duto oyie kuom lerno.  
\v 8 Johana owuon ne ok en ler nogo, to nobiro mana kaka janeno mar lerno. 
\p  
\v 9 Ler mar adier machiwo ler ni ji duto noyudo biro e piny e kindeno.  
\v 10 Ne en e piny, to kata obedo ni en ema nomiyo ochwe piny, to piny ne ok ongʼeye.  
\v 11 Nobiro ir joge owuon, to joge ne ok orwake.  
\v 12 To ji duto mane orwake, mi oyie kuome, nomiyogi teko mar doko nyithind Nyasaye,  
\v 13 ma gin nyithindo mane ok onywol koa e koth dhano, kata kuom pach dhano, kata kuom dwach dichwo, to nonywolgi kuom Nyasaye. 
\p  
\v 14 Wach nodoko dhano kendo nodak kodwa. Waseneno duongʼne, ma en duongʼ mar Wuowi ma Miderma, ma noa ka Wuoro kopongʼ gi ngʼwono kod adiera. 
\p  
\v 15 Johana notimo neno kuome. Nokok matek kowacho niya, “Ma e Jal mane awuoyo kuome kane awachonu ni, ‘Jal mabiro bangʼa oloya mabor nikech ne entie kapok ne abetie.’ ”  
\v 16 Waduto waseyudo gweth mogundho kuom ngʼwonone mathoth.  
\v 17 Chik nochiw kokalo kuom Musa, to ngʼwono kod adiera, to Yesu Kristo ema nokelo.  
\v 18 Onge ngʼama oseneno Nyasaye, to Wuowi ma Miderma machiegni gi Wuoro ema osemiyo wangʼeye. 
\s1 Johana ja-Batiso okwero ni ok en Kristo 
\p  
\v 19 Ma e neno mane Johana otimo ka jo-Yahudi modak Jerusalem nooro jodolo gi jo-Lawi mondo openje ni ne en ngʼa.  
\v 20 Johana ne ok opandonegi gimoro, to nohulonigi ka en thuolo niya, “Ok an Kristo.” 
\p  
\v 21 Negipenje niya, “Kare in ngʼa? In Elija koso?” 
\p To nowacho niya, “Ok an.” 
\p “Koso in e janabi?” 
\p Nodwoko niya, “Ooyo.” 
\p  
\v 22 Eka negiwachone mogik niya, “Kare, in ngʼa? Miwa dwoko mondo water ni joma ne oorowa. Iwacho angʼo kuomi in iwuon?” 
\p  
\v 23 Johana nodwokogi gi weche mag Isaya Janabi niya, “An e ngʼat makok e thim ni, ‘Losuru yo moriere tir ne Jehova Nyasaye.’ ”\f + \fr 1:23 \ft \xt Isa 40:3\f* 
\p  
\v 24 To jo-Farisai moko ma noor,  
\v 25 nopenje niya, “Ka ok in Kristo, kata Elija, kata janabi, to angʼo momiyo ibatiso ji?” 
\p  
\v 26 Johana nodwokogi niya, “An abatisou gi pi, to nitie ngʼato e dieru ma ukia.  
\v 27 En Jal mabiro bangʼa, ma ok awinjora gonyo tond wuochene.” 
\p  
\v 28 Magi duto notimore Bethania, loka mar aora Jordan, kuma Johana ne batisoe ji. 
\s1 Yesu nyarombo mar Nyasaye 
\p  
\v 29 Kinyne Johana noneno Yesu kabiro ire, mi nowacho niya, “Neuru, Jalcha e Nyarombo mar Nyasaye, magolo richo mar piny!  
\v 30 Ma e jal mane awuoyo kuome kane awacho ni, ‘Ngʼato mabiro bangʼa oloya mabor, nikech ne entie kapok ne abetie.’  
\v 31 An awuon ne ok angʼeye, to gimomiyo ne abiro ka abatiso ji gi pi ne en mondo ofwenyre ni Israel.” 
\p  
\v 32 Eka Johana notimo nenoni kama: “Ne aneno Roho kalor piny koa e polo e kido mar akuru kendo kapiyo kuome.  
\v 33 Ka dine Jal mane oora mondo abatis ji gi pi we nyisa, to dine ok angʼeye. Nonyisa ni, ‘Ngʼama ineno ka Roho olor mi opiyo kuome e Jal mabiro batiso ji gi Roho Maler.’  
\v 34 Koro aseneno mano kotimore omiyo anyisou ni en Wuod Nyasaye.” 
\s1 Jopuonjre mokwongo mag Yesu 
\p  
\v 35 Kinyne Johana ne ni kanyo kendo gi jopuonjrene ariyo.  
\v 36 Kane gineno ka Yesu kalo machiegni, nowacho niya, “Neuru, Jalcha e Nyarombo mar Nyasaye!” 
\p  
\v 37 Kane jopuonjrene ariyogo owinjo kowacho mano, negiluwo bangʼ Yesu.  
\v 38 Yesu nolokore monenogi ka giluwo bangʼe, mi nopenjogi niya, \wj “Angʼo mudwaro?”\wj* 
\p Negiwachone niya, “Rabi” (ma tiende ni “Japuonj”), “idak kanye?” 
\p  
\v 39 Nodwokogi niya, \wj “Biuru mondo udhi une.”\wj* 
\p Omiyo negidhi mine gineno kama ne odakie, kendo negibet kode kanyo odiechiengʼ ngima. Ne en kar sa apar mar odhiambo. 
\p  
\v 40 Andrea mowadgi Simon Petro ne en achiel kuom ji ariyo mane owinjo gima Johana nowacho mi noluwo bangʼ Yesu.  
\v 41 Gima Andrea notimo mokwongo ne en manyo owadgi ma Simon kendo nyise niya, “Waseyudo Mesia” (tiende ni Kristo).  
\v 42 Omiyo nokelo Simon ir Yesu. 
\p Yesu nongʼiye tir mowachone niya, \wj “In Simon wuod Johana, chiengʼ moro noluongi ni Kefa”\wj* (tiende ni Petro\f + \fr 1:42 \fq Kefa \ft en dho jo-Arama, to \fq Petro \ft en dho jo-Yunani, giduto tiende ni \fqa Lwanda.\f*). 
\s1 Yesu oluongo Filipo gi Nathaniel 
\p  
\v 43 Kinyne Yesu nongʼado e pache mondo oa odhi Galili. Kane oyudo Filipo, nowachone niya, \wj “Luwa.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 44 Filipo, mana kaka Andrea gi Petro, ne aa e dala mar Bethsaida.  
\v 45 Filipo noyudo Nathaniel mowachone niya, “Waseyudo ngʼat ma Musa nondiko kuome e kitap Chik, kendo ma jonabi bende nondiko kuome, ma en Yesu ja-Nazareth, ma wuod Josef.” 
\p  
\v 46 Nathaniel nopenje niya, “Bende gima ber moro amora nyalo aa Nazareth adier?” 
\p Filipo nodwoke niya, “Bi mondo ine.” 
\p  
\v 47 Kane Yesu oneno Nathaniel ka biro kochomo ire, nowuoyo kuome kowacho niya, \wj “Neuru ja-Israel adier, maonge miganga moro amora kuome.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 48 Nathaniel nopenje niya, “Ingʼeya nade?” 
\p Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Ne aneni sa ma ne in e tiend ngʼowu, kane pok Filipo oluongi.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 49 Eka Nathaniel nodwoke niya, “Rabi, in Wuod Nyasaye adier; in Ruodh Israel.” 
\p  
\v 50 Yesu nowachone niya, \wj “Iyie mana nikech aa wachoni ni nende aneni e tie yiend ngʼowu. To ibiro neno gik madongo mohingo mano.”\wj* 
\v 51 Eka nomedo wacho niya, \wj “Awachonu adier ni ubiro neno ka polo oyawore, kendo ka malaike mag Nyasaye idho kendo lor kuom Wuod Dhano.”\wj* 
\c 2  
\s1 Yesu oloko pi divai 
\p  
\v 1 Chiengʼ mar adek, arus moro ne nitie Kana, e piny Galili. Min Yesu ne ni kanyo,  
\v 2 kendo Yesu gi jopuonjrene bende noluongi e arusno.  
\v 3 Kane divai orumo, min Yesu nowachone niya, “Divai mane jogi nigo oserumo.” 
\p  
\v 4 Yesu nowachone niya, \wj “Mama, angʼo momiyo idwaro mondo atim ma to sana pok ochopo?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 5 Eka min-gi nowachone jotich niya, “Timuru gimoro amora monyisou.” 
\p  
\v 6 To machiegni kanyo ne nitie degi auchiel mag pi, mane gin kaka degi ma jo-Yahudi ne tiyogo kuom logo e yor pwodhruok, ma moro ka moro ne tingʼo pi madirom depe ariyo kata adek. 
\p  
\v 7 Yesu nowachone jotich niya, \wj “Pongʼuru degnigi gi pi”\wj*; mine gipongʼogi thich. 
\p  
\v 8 Eka nonyisogi niya, \wj “Koro tuomuru pi moko mondo ukaw uter ne jatend budho.”\wj* 
\p Negitimo kamano,  
\v 9 kendo jatend budho nobilo pi mane koro oselokore divai. Ne ok ofwenyo kuma ne ogolee, kata obedo ni jotich mane otuomo pi to nongʼeyo. Eka noluongo wuon kisera tenge,  
\v 10 kendo nowachone niya, “Ji mangʼeny kuongo kelo divai maber eka bangʼe gikelo divai maboth ka welo osemetho momer to in to ne ikano divai maber mogik nyaka sani.” 
\p  
\v 11 Ranyisi mar hono mokwongoni Yesu notimo e dala Kana e piny Galili. Nonyiso duongʼne kuom timne, kendo jopuonjrene noyie kuome. 
\s1 Yesu oriembo jo-ohala e hekalu 
\p  
\v 12 Bangʼ mano nodhi Kapernaum kaachiel gi min-gi gi owetene kod jopuonjrene. Negibet kuno kuom ndalo manok. 
\p  
\v 13 Ka kinde mag Pasaka mar jo-Yahudi ne chiegni chopo, Yesu nodhi Jerusalem.  
\v 14 To ei agola mag hekalu, noyudo ka ji hono dhok gi rombe kod akuche, kendo jomoko to nobet olworo mesni ka giwilo pesa.  
\v 15 Omiyo noloso del gi piende molir olir, kendo noriembo ji duto oko ei hekalu, kod rombe gi dhok bende. Nokeyo pesa mag jowil pesa, kendo noloko mesnigi ataro.  
\v 16 Johala mag akuche to nowachonegi niya, \wj “Goluru gigi oko ka! Ngʼa monyisou mondo ulok od Wuora chiro!”\wj* 
\v 17 Jopuonjrene noparo gima nondiki niya, “Hera matut ma aherogo odi tieka.”\f + \fr 2:17 \ft \xt Zab 69:9\f* 
\p  
\v 18 Eka jo-Yahudi nowachone niya, “Ranyisi mar hono mane minyalo nyisowa mondo osir teko mitimogo gigi?” 
\p  
\v 19 Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Mukuru hekaluni, to abiro gere kendo bangʼ ndalo adek.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 20 Jo-Yahudi nodwoke niya, “Gero hekaluni osekawo higni piero angʼwen gauchiel, to in to ere kaka inyalo gere gi ndalo adek?”  
\v 21 To hekalu mane owuoyo kuome ne en ringre.  
\v 22 Bangʼ kane osechier oa kuom joma otho, jopuonjrene noparo gima nowachono. Omiyo ne giyie kuom Ndiko kod weche mane Yesu osewacho. 
\p  
\v 23 Kane pod en Jerusalem e Sap Pasaka, ji mangʼeny noneno ranyisi mag honni mane otimo mine giyie kuom nyinge.  
\v 24 To Yesu ne ok ochiwore e lwetgi, nimar nongʼeyo pach ji duto.  
\v 25 Ne ok odwar mondo ngʼato onyise wach moro kuom dhano wadgi nimar nongʼeyo gik manie chuny dhano. 
\c 3  
\s1 Yesu owuoyo gi Nikodemo 
\p  
\v 1 Ne nitie ngʼat moro ma ja-Farisai ma nyinge Nikodemo, ne en achiel kuom jobuch jo-Yahudi.  
\v 2 Nikodemo nobiro ir Yesu gotieno mowachone niya, “Rabi, wangʼeyo ni in japuonj moa ka Nyasaye, nimar onge ngʼama nyalo timo ranyisi mag honni mitimogi ka Nyasaye ok ni kode.” 
\p  
\v 3 Yesu nodwoke kawacho niya, \wj “Awachoni adier, ni onge ngʼama nyalo neno pinyruoth Nyasaye ka ok onywole nywol manyien.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 4 Nikodemo nopenje niya, “Ere kaka inyalo nywol ngʼato kosebedo ngʼama duongʼ? Adier, bende dochak odog ei min mare mi chak nywole kendo!” 
\p  
\v 5 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Awachoni adier ni onge ngʼama nyalo donjo e pinyruoth Nyasaye ka ok onywole gi pi kod Roho Maler.\wj* 
\v 6 \wj Ringruok nywolo mana ringruok, to Roho nywolo roho.\wj* 
\v 7 \wj Ok onego ibwogi kuom gima awacho ni, ‘Nyaka nywoli nywol manyien.’\wj* 
\v 8 \wj Yamo futo kochomo kuma ohero, kendo inyalo winje, to ok inyal nyiso kuma oaye kata kuma odhiye. Mano bende e gima timore ni ngʼato ka ngʼato monywol kuom Roho.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 9 Nikodemo nopenje niya, “Gigo nyalo timore kamano nade?” 
\p  
\v 10 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Ere kaka ok iwinj tiend wechegi, to in japuonj jo-Israel?\wj* 
\v 11 \wj Anyisi adier ni wawuoyo kuom gik mwangʼeyo, kendo watimo neno kuom gik mwaseneno; to un, to pod utamoru rwako neno marwa.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Asewuoyo kodu mana kuom gik manie pinyni, to utamoru yie; koro ubiro yie nade ka awuoyo kuom gik manie polo?\wj* 
\v 13 \wj Onge ngʼato angʼata mosedhi e polo makmana Jal mane olor oa e polo, ma en Wuod Dhano.\wj* 
\v 14 \wj Mana kaka Musa nochungo thuol e thim, e kaka Wuod Dhano bende ibiro chungo,\wj* 
\v 15 \wj mondo ngʼato ka ngʼato moyie kuome obed gi ngima mochwere.\wj* 
\p  
\v 16 \wj “Nikech Nyasaye nohero piny ahinya, omiyo nochiwo Wuode ma miderma, mondo ngʼato angʼata moyie kuome kik lal, to obed gi ngima mochwere.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Nimar Nyasaye ne ok ooro Wuode e piny mondo ongʼad ne piny bura, to noore mondo ores piny.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Ngʼato angʼata moyie kuome ok nobed gi bura. To ngʼat ma ok oyie kuome bura oseloyo, nikech pok oyie kuom nying Wuowi ma miderma mar Nyasaye.\wj* 
\v 19 \wj Ma e gima bura osengʼado: Ler osebiro e piny, to ji nohero mudho moloyo ler, nikech timbegi ne richo.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj Ngʼato ka ngʼato matimo richo ok dwar ler, kendo ok odwar donjo ei ler, nikech oluor ni dipo ka timbene ongʼere.\wj* 
\v 21 \wj To ngʼato angʼata mawuotho e adiera donjo e ler, mondo onere maler ni gik motimo duto gin gik ma Nyasaye oyiego.”\wj* 
\s1 Johana ja-Batiso otimo neno kuom Yesu 
\p  
\v 22 Bangʼ mano, Yesu gi jopuonjrene nodhi e gwenge mag piny Judea, kendo nokawo kinde mogwarore kodgi kuno, kobatiso ji.  
\v 23 To Johana bende ne batiso ji Ainon machiegni gi Salim, nikech pi ne ngʼeny kanyo, kendo ji nosiko ka biro ire mondo obatisgi.  
\v 24 (Mano notimore ka Johana ne pok oter e od twech.)  
\v 25 Mino wach nochakore e kind jopuonjre Johana moko gi ja-Yahudi moro kuom wach mar pwodhruok.  
\v 26 Negibiro ir Johana mi giwachone niya, “Rabi, jal manyocha ni kodi loka Jordan, ma en Jal mane iwuoyo kuome cha, parie ni en bende tinde obatiso ji, kendo ji duto dhi ire.” 
\p  
\v 27 Johana nodwokogi niya, “Onge gima ngʼato nyalo yudo makmana mano momiye koa e polo.  
\v 28 Un uwegi unyalo timo neno ni ne anyisou ni, ‘An ok an Kristo, to an ngʼat moor mondo otel nyime.’  
\v 29 Miaha en mar wuon kisera. Jachungʼ mar wuon kisera nyaka chik ite ne wuon kisera kendo winje; opongʼ gi mor kowinjo dwond wuon kisera kawuoyo. An ema an gi mor machal kamano, kendo mornano koro oromo chuth.  
\v 30 En ema nyaka omed yudo duongʼ moloyo, to an nyaka adog piny. 
\p  
\v 31 “Jal moa e polo malo duongʼ moloyo gik moko duto, to ngʼat monywol e piny en mar piny, kendo owuoyo kaka ngʼama onywol e piny. Jal moa e polo duongʼ moloyo gik moko duto.  
\v 32 Otimo neno kuom gik moseneno kendo owinjo, to onge ngʼama orwako nende.  
\v 33 Ngʼat moyie ni wechene gin adier, biro ngʼeyo malongʼo ni Nyasaye en ja-adiera.  
\v 34 Nimar Jal ma Nyasaye oseoro wacho weche Nyasaye, nikech Nyasaye chiwo Rohone mogundho ma ok ongʼwonyo lwete.  
\v 35 Wuoro ohero Wuowi, kendo oseketo gik moko duto e lwete.  
\v 36 Ngʼato moyie kuom Wuowi nigi ngima mochwere, to ngʼat modagi Wuowi ok none ngimano, nimar mirimb Nyasaye osiko kuome.” 
\c 4  
\s1 Yesu owuoyo gi chi Samaria 
\p  
\v 1 Jo-Farisai nowinjo ni joma Yesu ne oseloko obedo jopuonjre, kendo obatiso ne ngʼeny moloyo jopuonjre Johana,  
\v 2 kata obedo ni Yesu owuon ne ok batiso ji, to jopuonjrene ema ne timo kamano.  
\v 3 Kane Ruoth owinjo wachni, noa Judea mochako odok Galili. 
\p  
\v 4 To nochune ni nyaka okadh e piny Samaria.  
\v 5 Kuom mano, nochopo e dala moro e piny Samaria miluongo ni Sukar, mane ni machiegni gi puodho mane Jakobo omiyo Josef wuode.  
\v 6 Soko Jakobo ne ni kanyo, kendo Yesu ne koro ool gi wuoth, omiyo nobet piny e dir sokono. Ne en kar sa auchiel mar odiechiengʼ. 
\p  
\v 7 E sechego chi Samaria moro nobiro umbo pi, mi Yesu nowachone niya, \wj “Yie imiya pi amodhi.”\wj* 
\v 8 (Mano noyudo ka jopuonjrene osedhi Sukar mondo ongʼiew chiemo.) 
\p  
\v 9 Chi Samaria-no nowachone niya, “In ja-Yahudi, an to an chi Samaria. Ere kaka ikwaya pi modho?” (Donge ingʼeyo ni jo-Yahudi ok winjre gi jo-Samaria.) 
\p  
\v 10 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Ka dine ingʼe mich Nyasaye kendo ingʼe jal makwayi pi mondo omodhi, to dikwaye pi momiyi pi mar ngima.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 11 Dhakono nowachone niya, “Jaduongʼ, ionge gi gima inyalo tuomogo pi, kendo sokoni bende tut. Pi ngimano to inyalo yud kanye?  
\v 12 Iparo ni iduongʼ moloyo Jakobo kwarwa mane omiyowa sokoni, kendo nomodho pige en owuon kaachiel gi yawuote, gi jambe kod dhoge?” 
\p  
\v 13 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Ngʼato ka ngʼato mamodho pigni riyo biro chako loye,\wj* 
\v 14 \wj to ngʼato angʼata momodho pi mamiye ok nochak owinj riyo. Chutho, pi ma anamiye nodok soko mar pi e iye, mosiko ka bubni nyaka chop e ngima mochwere.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 15 Dhakono nowachone niya, “Jaduongʼ, yie imiyae pigno mondo riyo kik chak loya, kendo kik asik ka achandora gi biro ka pile pile mondo aom pi.” 
\p  
\v 16 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Dhi iluong chwori eka iduogi.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 17 Nodwoke niya, “Aonge gi dichwo.” 
\p Yesu nowachone niya, \wj “In kare kuom wacho ni ionge gi dichwo.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Adiera en ni isebedo gi chwo abich, kendo ngʼat makoro in-go sani bende ok chwori. Gima isewachono en adier.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 19 Dhakono nowachone niya, “Jaduongʼ, nenorena ni in janabi.  
\v 20 Kwerewa ne lemo ewi godni, to un jo-Yahudi to uwacho ka uramo ni Jerusalem ema nyaka walamie.” 
\p  
\v 21 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Nyarwa, yie koda; ndalo biro ma ok unulam Wuoro ewi godni kata ei Jerusalem.\wj* 
\v 22 \wj Un jo-Samaria ulamo gima ukia, nimar warruok aa kuom jo-Yahudi.\wj* 
\v 23 \wj Kata kamano kinde biro, kendo osechopo, ma joma lemo gadier nolam Wuoro e yo ma Roho dwaro kendo gadiera, joma lamo kamano ema Wuoro dwaro.\wj* 
\v 24 \wj Nyasaye en Roho, omiyo joma lame nyaka lame e yo ma Roho dwaro kendo gadiera.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 25 Dhakono nowacho niya, “Angʼeyo ni in Mesia” (miluongo ni Kristo) “mane onego bi kendo ka obiro, to enonyiswa tiend weche duto.” 
\p  
\v 26 Eka Yesu nonyise ratiro niya, \wj “An ma awuoyo kodini An e En.”\wj* 
\s1 Jopuonjre odwogo ir Yesu 
\p  
\v 27 E sechego jopuonjrene noduogo, kendo ne giwuoro kane giyude kowuoyo gi dhako. To onge ngʼama nopenjo niya, “Angʼo midwaro kuom dhakoni?” kata niya, “Iwuoyo kode nangʼo?” 
\p  
\v 28 Eka dhakono noweyo dapige kanyo, kendo nowuok odok dala mi owachone ji niya,  
\v 29 “Biuru uneye ngʼama osenyisa gik moko duto ma asetimo. Donge jalni dibed Kristo?”  
\v 30 Joma odak e dalano duto nowuok kadhi ire. 
\p  
\v 31 To e sechego jopuonjrene nosiko kajiwe niya, “Rabi, chamie gimoro.” 
\p  
\v 32 To nowachonegi niya, \wj “An gi chiemo ma achamo ma ukia gimoro amora kuome.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 33 Eka jopuonjrene nowacho e kindgi giwegi niya, “Dibed ni ngʼato osekelone chiemo?” 
\p  
\v 34 Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “Chiemba en timo dwach Jal mane oora kendo tieko tichne.\wj* 
\v 35 \wj Donge uwacho ni, ‘Odongʼ dweche angʼwen to ndalo keyo chopo’? Awachonu ni utingʼ wengeu malo urang puothe! Gisechiek giromo keyo.\wj* 
\v 36 \wj Kata mana sani ngʼat ma keyo ichulo pokne, kendo ochoko olembe mochiek ne ngima mochwere, mondo omi jachwoyo, kaachiel gi jakeyo, obed mamor kanyakla.\wj* 
\v 37 \wj Mana kaka ngero mawacho ni, ‘Ngʼato achiel chwoyo, to ngʼato machielo keyo’ en adier.\wj* 
\v 38 \wj Ne aorou mondo uka gima ne ok utiyone. Jomoko nono osetiyo tich matek moloyo, to un useyudo konyruok kuom tichgi matek.”\wj* 
\s1 Jo-Samaria mangʼeny oyie kuom Yesu 
\p  
\v 39 Jo-Samaria mangʼeny moa e dalano noyie kuom Yesu nikech neno mane dhakono otimonigi kowacho niya, “Ne onyisa gik moko duto ma asetimo.”  
\v 40 Kuom mano, ka jo-Samaria nobiro ir Yesu, negisaye mondo omed bet kodgi, mi nobet kodgi kuom ndalo ariyo.  
\v 41 Omiyo ji mangʼeny moko bende noyie kuom Yesu nikech weche mane owachonegi. 
\p  
\v 42 Negiwachone dhakono niya, “Koro wayie, ok nikech weche mane iwacho kende; to wasewinje gi itwa wawegi, kendo wangʼeyo gadier ni jalni en Jawar mar piny.” 
\s1 Yesu ochango wuod jatelo moro 
\p  
\v 43 Bangʼ ndalo ariyogo, nowuok modhi Galili.  
\v 44 (Mano noyudo ka Yesu owuon nosewacho ni janabi ok mi duongʼ e pinygi owuon.)  
\v 45 Kane ochopo Galili, jo-Galili norwake. Ne giseneno gik moko duto mane osetimo Jerusalem chiengʼ Sap Pasaka, nimar gin bende ne gin kuno. 
\p  
\v 46 Nochako olimo dala mar Kana, manie piny Galili, kama ne oloke pi divai. To ne nitie jatelo moro ma wuode ne tuo Kapernaum.  
\v 47 Kane ngʼatni owinjo ni Yesu osechopo Galili koa Judea, nodhi ire mosaye mondo odhi ochang wuode mane chiegni tho. 
\p  
\v 48 Yesu nowachone niya, \wj “Angʼeyo ni ka ok uneno honni gi ranyisi, to ok ubi yie.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 49 Jatelono nowachone niya, “Jaduongʼ, yie idhi koda kapok nyathina otho.” 
\p  
\v 50 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Dhiyo, wuodi dhi bedo mangima.”\wj* 
\p Ngʼatno norwako wach mane Yesu owachoneno, mi noa odhi.  
\v 51 Kane oyudo pod en e yo odok dalane, jotichne noromone gi wach ni wuode koro ngima.  
\v 52 Kane ononogi mondo ongʼe ni en sa mane mane wuode ochangoe, negiwachone niya, “Midhusi nyoro oweye kar sa abiriyo.” 
\p  
\v 53 Eka wuon nongʼeyo ni mano e sa nogono mane Yesu owachone niya, \wj “Wuodi dhi bedo mangima.”\wj* Kuom mano, en kaachiel gi joode duto ne giyie kuom Yesu. 
\p  
\v 54 Mano e hono mar ariyo mane Yesu otimo, ka nodonjo Galili koa Judea. 
\c 5  
\s1 Yesu ochango ngʼat matuo Bethesda 
\p  
\v 1 Bangʼ kinde moko, Yesu nodhi Jerusalem e Sap jo-Yahudi.  
\v 2 E Jerusalem kanyo, but ranga Rombe, miluongo ni Bethesda gi dho jo-Hibrania, ne nitiere yawo moro ma nigi raidhi abich midonjogo.  
\v 3 Kanyo ji mathoth man-gi tuoche mopogore opogore kaka muofni, rongʼonde, kod joma nigi athany nohero riyo kanyo [kendo negirito mondo pi otugre.  
\v 4 Kinde ka kinde malaika mar Ruoth ne lor mondo otug pi. Ngʼama nokwongo donjo e pigno sa ma otugoreno ne chango kuom kit tuo moro amora mane en-go].\f + \fr 5:4 \ft Loko moko machon mag Muma onge gi giko mar \xt 5:3\ft  kod \xt 5:4\ft  duto.\f* 
\v 5 To ne nitie ngʼato kanyo mane osebedo gi midekre kuom higni piero adek gaboro.  
\v 6 Kane Yesu onene konindo kanyo, kendo kane onyise ni osebedo kochal kamano kuom kinde marabora, nopenje niya, \wj “Bende idwaro ni ochangi?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 7 Ngʼatno nodwoke niya, “Jaduongʼ, aonge gi ngʼama nyalo konya donjo ei yawo sa ma pi otugore. Kinde ka kinde ma atemo ni adonji to ngʼat machielo donjo kuongona.” 
\p  
\v 8 Yesu nowachone niya, \wj “Aa malo! Kaw pieni mondo iwuothi.”\wj* 
\v 9 Gikanyono ngʼatno nochango, kendo nokawo piende mowuotho. 
\p Ma notimore chiengʼ Sabato,  
\v 10 omiyo jo-Yahudi nowachone ngʼama nochangino niya, “Kawuono en chiengʼ Sabato, kendo chik ok oyieni tingʼo pieni.” 
\p  
\v 11 Nodwokogi niya, “Ngʼat ma nochanga ema nowachona ni, ‘Kaw pieni mondo iwuothi.’ ” 
\p  
\v 12 Omiyo negipenje niya, “Mano to en ngʼama nade manowachoni ni ikaw pieni kendo iwuothi?” 
\p  
\v 13 To ngʼat mane ochangino ne ok ongʼeyo nying ngʼat mane ochange, nimar noyudo ka Yesu osedonjo ei oganda mane ni kanyo. 
\p  
\v 14 Bangʼe Yesu noyude e hekalu mowachone niya, \wj “Winji, koro isedoko mangima. We richo, nono to gimoro marach moloyo biro timoreni.”\wj* 
\v 15 Ngʼatno noa modhi onyiso jo-Yahudi ni Yesu ema nochange. 
\s1 Ngima miyudo kuom Wuowi 
\p  
\v 16 Kuom mano, nikech Yesu ne chango ji chiengʼ Sabato, jo-Yahudi nosande.  
\v 17 To Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “Wuora osiko katiyo tichne nyaka kawuono, kendo an bende atiyo mana kamano.”\wj* 
\v 18 Wachni nomiyo jo-Yahudi oramo ni nyaka ginege, nimar negineno ni ok Sabato kende ema noketho, to bende noluongo Nyasaye ni Wuon-gi, manyiso ni ne oketore ni orom gi Nyasaye. 
\p  
\v 19 Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Awachonu adier ni, Wuod Dhano ok nyal timo gimoro kende owuon; to onyalo mana timo gima oneno ka Wuoro timo, nikech gimoro amora ma Wuoro timo ema Wuowi bende timo.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj Nimar Wuoro ohero Wuowi, kendo onyise gik moko duto motimo. Ee, obiro medo nyise nyaka gik madongo moloyo magi mi unuwuor.\wj* 
\v 21 \wj Mana kaka Wuoro chiero joma otho, kendo miyogi ngima, e kaka Wuowi bende chiwo ngima ne ngʼato angʼata mohero.\wj* 
\v 22 \wj To bende, Wuoro ok ngʼad bura ne ngʼato, to oseketo teko mar ngʼado bura e lwet Wuowi,\wj* 
\v 23 \wj mondo ji duto omi Wuowi duongʼ mana kaka gimiyo Wuoro duongʼ. Ngʼat ma ok mi Wuowi duongʼ ok mi Wuoro mane ooro Wuowino duongʼ.\wj* 
\p  
\v 24 \wj “Awachonu adier ni ngʼato angʼata mawinjo wachna, kendo moyie kuom Jal mane oora, nigi ngima mochwere, kendo ok bi ngʼadne buch tho; to osengʼado oa e tho modonjo e ngima.\wj* 
\v 25 \wj Awachonu adier ni ndalo biro, kendo koro osechopo, ma joma otho biro winjo dwond Wuod Nyasaye, kendo joma owinjo dwolno biro doko mangima.\wj* 
\v 26 \wj Mana kaka Wuoro nigi teko mar miyo ji ngima, e kaka osemiyo Wuowi bende teko mar timo kamano.\wj* 
\v 27 \wj To bende osemiye teko mondo ongʼad bura, nikech en e Wuod Dhano.\wj* 
\p  
\v 28 \wj “Wachni kik bwogu, nimar ndalo biro ma ji duto manie bur nowinj dwonde\wj* 
\v 29 \wj mi giwuog oko; joma osetimo maber nochier mondo obed mangima, to joma osetimo gik maricho nochier mondo ongʼadnigi buch tho.\wj* 
\v 30 \wj An onge gima anyalo timo gi tekona awuon, to angʼado bura ne ji mana kaluwore gi gima awinjo, kendo bura ma angʼado nikare, nimar ok atim kamano mondo atim dwarona awuon, to mondo atim dwaro Jal mane oora.\wj* 
\s1 Weche manyiso ni Yesu en ngʼa 
\p  
\v 31 \wj “Kapo ni atimo nenda awuon to nenda ok nikare.\wj* 
\v 32 \wj To nitie ngʼama chielo matimo neno ma chwaka, kendo angʼeyo ni neno motimo kuoma nikare.\wj* 
\p  
\v 33 \wj “Ne uoro joote ne Johana kendo osetimo neno kuom adiera.\wj* 
\v 34 \wj Ok awach kamano nikech ayie gi nend dhano, to awacho kamano mondo uyud warruok.\wj* 
\v 35 \wj Johana ne en taya maliel makelo ler, kendo kuom kinde moko nuyie mondo omiu lerno.\wj* 
\p  
\v 36 \wj “To an gi neno maduongʼ moloyo mar Johana, nimar tich mane Wuora omiya mondo achopi, kendo makoro atimo sani-ni, nyiso ni Wuora ema noora.\wj* 
\v 37 \wj Wuoro moseorano osetimo neno kuoma en owuon. Pok uwinjo dwonde nyaka nene kendo pok uneno kite.\wj* 
\v 38 \wj Wachne bende onge eiu, nimar udagi yie kuom Jal mane ooro.\wj* 
\v 39 \wj Uketo chunyu kuom nono Muma nikech uparo ni unyalo yudo ngima mochwere kuomgi. Muma ema timo neno kuoma,\wj* 
\v 40 \wj to kata kamano utamoru biro ira mondo uyud ngima.\wj* 
\p  
\v 41 \wj “An ok adwar mondo dhano omiya duongʼ;\wj* 
\v 42 \wj nikech angʼeyou maber ni uonge gihera mar Nyasaye e chunyu.\wj* 
\v 43 \wj An asebiro e nying Wuora, to utamoru rwaka; to ka ngʼato machielo nobi e nyinge owuon to ubiro rwake arwaka.\wj* 
\v 44 \wj Ere kaka unyalo yie ka urwako pak ma joweteu pakougo, to ok utem matek mondo uyud pak moa kuom Nyasaye ma achiel kende?\wj* 
\p  
\v 45 \wj “Kik upar ni abiro donjonu e nyim Wuoro. Ngʼat madonjonu en Musa, ma useketo genou kuome.\wj* 
\v 46 \wj To ka dine bed ni uyie kuom Musa, to An bende dine uyie kuoma, nimar nondiko kuoma.\wj* 
\v 47 \wj To kaka ok uyie kuom gik mane ondiko, ere kaka ubiro yie kuom gik ma awacho?”\wj* 
\c 6  
\s1 Yesu opidho ji alufu abich 
\p  
\v 1 Bangʼ kinde moko, Yesu nodhi nyaka loka machielo mar Nam Galili (tiende ni Nam Tiberia),  
\v 2 kendo oganda maduongʼ noluwe nikech ne giseneno honni mane osetimo kochango joma tuo.  
\v 3 Eka Yesu nodhi e bath got kamoro mi nobet piny kanyo gi jopuonjrene.  
\v 4 Sap Pasaka mar jo-Yahudi koro nokayo machiegni. 
\p  
\v 5 Kane Yesu otingʼo wangʼe noneno oganda maduongʼ kabiro ire, mowachone Filipo niya, \wj “Ere kuma wanyalo ngʼiewe makati ni jogi mondo gicham?”\wj* 
\v 6 Nopenje kamano mana mondo otemego nimar nongʼeyo gima nobiro timo. 
\p  
\v 7 Filipo nodwoke niya, “Kata chudo mar ngʼato mar dweche aboro ok dingʼiewgo makati moromo, ma ngʼato ka ngʼato kuom jogi duto nyalo yudo kata matin!” 
\p  
\v 8 Japuonjrene machielo, ma nyinge Andrea, mane en owadgi Simon Petro nowachone niya,  
\v 9 “Wuowi moro eri nika man-gi makati matindo abich motedi gi shairi, kod rech matindo ariyo, to magi dikony angʼo kuom pidho oganda machal kama?” 
\p  
\v 10 Yesu nowacho niya, \wj “Nyisuru ji obed piny.”\wj* Kanyo ne nitie lum mangʼeny, omiyo ji nobedo piny (ka joma chwo kuomgi noromo ji alufu abich).  
\v 11 Eka Yesu nokawo makatigo mi nogwedhogi, bangʼe opogone joma nobedo piny, kendo ngʼato ka ngʼato nochiemo kaka odwaro. Kamano bende e kaka notimo gi rechgo. 
\p  
\v 12 Kane gisechiemo giduto mi giyiengʼ, nowachone jopuonjrene niya, \wj “Chokuru ngʼinjo duto ma ji ochamo oweyo. Kik uwe gimoro dhi nono.”\wj* 
\v 13 Omiyo negichokogi, kendo negipongʼo okepe apar gariyo gi ngʼinjo ma noa e makati matindo abich mane olos gi shairi, mane joma nosechiemo oweyo. 
\p  
\v 14 Kane ji oneno tim hono ma Yesu notimono, negichako wacho niya, “Kuom adier, ma e janabi mane onego bi e piny.”  
\v 15 To kaka Yesu nongʼeyo ni negichano biro make mondo gikete ruoth githuon, noa kanyo kendo nodhi ewi got moro kar kende. 
\s1 Yesu owuotho ewi pi 
\p  
\v 16 Kane ochopo odhiambo, jopuonjre nodhi nyaka e dho nam,  
\v 17 kuma negidonjo ei yie, kendo ne gisiayo yieno mi gingʼado nam nyaka Kapernaum. Sechego piny koro noselil, to Yesu ne pok obiro irgi.  
\v 18 Yamb ahiti ne kudho, kendo pi nam ne gingore matek.  
\v 19 Kane koro gisekiewo yie kama nyalo romo kilomita abich kata auchiel; negineno Yesu kawuotho ewi pi kochiko irgi; mi luoro nomakogi.  
\v 20 Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “Kik uluor, en mana An.”\wj* 
\v 21 Kane osewacho kamano eka ne gikwaye mondo odonj irgi ei yie. Kendo gikanyono yie nogowo e dho nam kama negidhiye. 
\p  
\v 22 Kinyne, oganda mane ni kode loka nam noyudo ni yie achiel kende ema ne ni kanyo, kendo ni Yesu ne ok odonjo ei yieno gi jopuonjrene, to ni negidhi adhiya kendgi.  
\v 23 Eka yiedhi moko moa Tiberia nogowo but kama ne ji ochame makati, mane Ruoth Yesu ogwedho.  
\v 24 Kane ogandano ofwenyo ni Yesu gi jopuonjrene ne onge kanyo, negidonjo ei yiedhigo, mi gidhi Kapernaum, mondo gimany Yesu kuno. 
\s1 Yesu e makati mar ngima 
\p  
\v 25 Kane giyude loka nam komachielo, negipenje niya, “Rabi, ne ichopo sa adi?” 
\p  
\v 26 Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Awachonu adier, ni umanya ok nikech nyoro uneno honni, to mana nikech makati manyoro uchamo ma uyiengʼ.\wj* 
\v 27 \wj Weuru tiyo ni chiemo marumo, to tiuru ni chiemo masiko nyaka chop uyud ngima mochwere, ma Wuod Dhano biro miyou. Nyasaye Wuoro oseketo kido mare kuome manyiso ni oyie kode.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 28 Eka negipenje niya, “Angʼo mowinjore watim eka wati tije ma Nyasaye dwaro?” 
\p  
\v 29 Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Tich ma Nyasaye dwaro en ni mondo uyie kuom Jal moseoro.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 30 Kuom mano negipenje niya, “Kara en hono mane ma idwaro timo mondo wane eka wayie kuomi? Angʼo mibiro timonwa?  
\v 31 Kwerewa nochamo manna e thim; mana kaka ondiki ni, ‘Nomiyogi chiemo moa e polo mondo gicham.’\f + \fr 6:31 \ft \xt Wuo 16:4; Neh 9:15; Zab 78:24,25\f*” 
\p  
\v 32 Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “Awachonu adier ni Musa ok ema nomiyou makati moa e polo, to Wuora ema nomiyou makati mar adier moa e polo.\wj* 
\v 33 \wj Nimar makati ma Nyasaye chiwo en Jal malor koa e polo kendo ochiwo ngimane ni piny.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 34 Negiwachone niya, “Jaduongʼ, miwae makati pile pile kochakore kawuono.” 
\p  
\v 35 Eka Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “An e makati mar ngima. Ngʼama obiro ira kech ok noka, kendo ngʼama oyie kuoma riyo ok nolo ngangʼ.\wj* 
\v 36 \wj To mana kaka nyocha anyisou, usenena to pod udagi yie kuoma.\wj* 
\v 37 \wj Joma Wuoro omiya duto biro ira, kendo ngʼato angʼata mobiro ira ok anariembi ngangʼ.\wj* 
\v 38 \wj Nimar asebiro e piny ka aa e polo, ok ni mondo atim dwacha, to mondo atim dwach Jal mane oora.\wj* 
\v 39 \wj Dwach Jal mane oora en ni kik awit kata achiel kuom ji duto mosemiya, to ni mondo achiergi chiengʼ giko.\wj* 
\v 40 \wj Adier, Wuora dwaro ni mondo ji duto mogeno kuom Wuowi, kendo moyie kuome mondo obed gi ngima mochwere, kendo ochiergi chiengʼ giko piny.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 41 Jo-Yahudi nochako ngʼur kode nikech nowacho niya, \wj “An e makati mobiro e piny koa e polo.”\wj* 
\v 42 Negiwacho niya, “Donge ma en Yesu, ma wuod Josef, ma wangʼeyo wuon gi min? Ere kaka dobukre kowacho sani ni, \wj ‘Ne abiro e piny ka aa e polo’\wj* ?” 
\p  
\v 43 Kuom mano, Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Weuru ngʼur e kindu uwegi.\wj* 
\v 44 \wj Onge ngʼama nyalo biro ira ka ok Wuora mane oora ema okele, kendo anachiere chiengʼ giko piny.\wj* 
\v 45 \wj Ondiki e kitepe Jonabi ni, ‘Jehova Nyasaye nopuonj ji duto.’\wj*\f + \fr 6:45 \ft \xt Isa 54:13\f*\wj Emomiyo ngʼat mosewinjo wach Wuoro, kod mosemako puonj mare, biro ira.\wj* 
\v 46 \wj Onge ngʼama oseneno Wuoro makmana Jal ma noa ka Nyasaye; En kende ema oseneno Wuoro.\wj* 
\v 47 \wj Awachonu adier ni ngʼama oyie kuoma nigi ngima mochwere.\wj* 
\v 48 \wj An e kuon mar ngima.\wj* 
\v 49 \wj Kwereu nochamo manna e thim, to kata kamano ne githo.\wj* 
\v 50 \wj An to awuoyo kuom makati moa e polo, ma ngʼato nyalo chamo mondo kik otho.\wj* 
\v 51 \wj An e makati mar ngima ma nobiro e piny koa e polo. Ka ngʼato moro amora ochamo makatini, to obiro bet mangima nyaka chiengʼ. Makatini en ringra, ma abiro chiwo mondo piny oyud ngima.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 52 Eka jo-Yahudi nochako mino wach e kindgi giwegi, kagiwacho niya, “Ere kaka ngʼatni nyalo miyowa ringre mondo wacham?” 
\p  
\v 53 Eka Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “Awachonu adier, ni ka ok uchamo ringre Wuod Dhano kendo umadho rembe, to uonge gi ngima.\wj* 
\v 54 \wj Ngʼato angʼata mochamo ringra kendo omadho remba nigi ngima mochwere, kendo abiro chiere chiengʼ giko piny.\wj* 
\v 55 \wj Ringra e chiemo madier kendo remba e math madier.\wj* 
\v 56 \wj Ngʼato angʼata mochamo ringra kendo omadho remba siko kuoma, to an bende asiko kuome.\wj* 
\v 57 \wj Mana kaka Wuoro Mangima noora, kendo angima nikech Wuoro, e kaka ngʼama chamo ringra biro bedo mangima nikech an.\wj* 
\v 58 \wj An e makati mobiro e piny koa e polo. Kwereu nochamo manna kendo ne githo, to ngʼat mochamo makatini, to biro bedo mangima nyaka chiengʼ.”\wj* 
\v 59 Nowacho wechegi Kapernaum kane oyudo opuonjo ei sinagogi. 
\s1 Jopuonjre mangʼeny oweyo Yesu 
\p  
\v 60 Kane jopuonjre owinjo wachno, thothgi nowacho niya, “Ma en puonj matek manade. En ngʼa manyalo yie gi puonjni?” 
\p  
\v 61 Yesu nongʼeyo ni jopuonjrene ne ngʼur kuom wachni, omiyo nowachonegi niya, \wj “Dibed ni wachni ochwanyou?\wj* 
\v 62 \wj Ka en kamano, to ubiro timoru nade ka unune Wuod Dhano kadok kuma ne oae!\wj* 
\v 63 \wj Roho ema chiwo ngima; to dhano ok nyal gimoro. Weche ma asewachonu gin mag Roho kod ngima.\wj* 
\v 64 \wj To kata kamano pod nitie jomoko kuomu ma ok oyie.”\wj* Yesu nowacho kamano nikech nosengʼeyo nyaka aa chakruok joma ok oyie kaachiel gi ngʼat mabiro ndhoge.  
\v 65 Eka nomedo wuoyo kowacho niya, \wj “Mano emomiyo ne anyisou ni onge ngʼama nyalo biro ira ka ok Wuora ema okele.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 66 Chakre kindeno ngʼeny jopuonjrene nodok chien moweyo luwe. 
\p  
\v 67 Yesu nopenjo jopuonjrene apar gariyo niya, \wj “Dibed ni un bende udwaro weya koso?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 68 Simon Petro nodwoke niya, “Ruoth, en ngʼa madwadhi ire? In ema in gi weche makelo ngima mochwere.  
\v 69 Wayie kendo wangʼeyo ni in e Ngʼama Ler mar Nyasaye.” 
\p  
\v 70 Eka Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Donge aseyierou duto karu ji apar gariyo, to kata kamano, ngʼato achiel kuomu en jachien!”\wj* 
\v 71 (Nowuoyo kuom Judas ma wuod Simon Iskariot mane biro ndhoge bangʼe, kata obedo ni ne en achiel kuom jopuonjrene apar gariyo.) 
\c 7  
\s1 Yesu odhi e Sap Kiche 
\p  
\v 1 Bangʼ mano Yesu nodhi koni gi koni e piny Galili, kotemo bedo mabor gi Judea nikech jo-Yahudi ne rite kuno mondo ginege.  
\v 2 To ka Sap jo-Yahudi mar Kiche ne chiegni chopo,  
\v 3 owete Yesu nowachone niya, “Wuog ka idhi Judea mondo jopuonjreni one honni mitimo.  
\v 4 Ka ngʼato dwaro mondo obed rahuma to ok otim gik moko lingʼ-lingʼ. Omiyo kaka isebedo ka itimo honnigi, koro nyenyri ane e lela mondo piny oneni.”  
\v 5 Negiwachone kamano nikech kata gin giwegi ne ok giyie kuome. 
\p  
\v 6 Kuom mano, Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “An sechega pok ochopo, un to unyalo timo gigeu sa moro amora.\wj* 
\v 7 \wj Piny ok nyal chayou, to an to piny ochaya nikech ahulo ni gik motimo richo.\wj* 
\v 8 \wj Un dhiuru adhiya e sawo. An pod ok adhi e sawono mondi nikech sa mowinjore adhi kuno pok ochopo.”\wj* 
\v 9 Bangʼ wacho kamano nodongʼ Galili. 
\p  
\v 10 Kata kamano bangʼ ka owetene nosewuok odhi e sawo, en bende nodhi, to nodhi lingʼ-lingʼ ka ji ok ongʼeyo ni odhi.  
\v 11 Jo-Yahudi ne manye e sawono ka gipenjo niya, “Ere ngʼatno?” 
\p  
\v 12 Ji mathoth mane ni e sawono ne wuoyo kuom Yesu. Jomoko nowacho niya, “En ngʼat maber.” 
\p To jomoko kuomgi to nowacho niya, “Ooyo, owuondo ji.”  
\v 13 To onge ngʼama ne nyalo hedhore wuoyo kuome e lela nikech negiluoro jo-Yahudi. 
\s1 Yesu opuonjo e Sawo 
\p  
\v 14 Kane ji pod ni e Sawo, Yesu nodonjo nyaka e laru mar hekalu mochako puonjo ji.  
\v 15 Jo-Yahudi nowuoro ka gipenjo niya, “Rieko machalo kama ngʼatni oyudo kanye to ok osomo?” 
\p  
\v 16 Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Gik ma apuonjo ok gin maga awuon, to gin mag Jal mane oora.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Ka ngʼato oyiero mar timo dwach Nyasaye, to obiro ngʼeyo ka bende puonjna oa kuom Nyasaye adier, kata ka awacho mana wechena awuon.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Ngʼat ma wuoyo kuome owuon timo kamano mondo oyud duongʼ en owuon, to ngʼat matiyo mondo Nyasaye mane oore ema oyud duongʼ, en ja-adiera, kendo onge miriambo moro amora kuome.\wj* 
\v 19 \wj Musa donge nomiyou chik? Kata kamano, onge kata achiel kuomu ma orito chik. Ka en kamano, to angʼo momiyo udwaro nega?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 20 Ogandano nodwoko niya, “Jachien ni kodi! En ngʼa madwaro negi?” 
\p  
\v 21 Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “Hono achiel kende ema ne atimo mi ubwok uduto.\wj* 
\v 22 \wj Nikech Musa nomiyou chik mar mondo oteru nyangu (to chutho Musa ok ema nomiyou chikni, to noa kuom kwereu), omiyo utero ji nyangu nyaka chiengʼ Sabato.\wj* 
\v 23 \wj To ka inyalo ter nyathi nyangu chiengʼ Sabato, mondo kik uketh Chik Musa, anto iu wangʼ koda nangʼo ka achango ringre dhano duto chiengʼ Sabato?\wj* 
\v 24 \wj Weuru ngʼado bura kuom gik muneno gioko, to ngʼaduru bura makare.”\wj* 
\s1 Bende Yesu en Kristo adier? 
\p  
\v 25 Gikanyono jo-Jerusalem moko nochako penjo niya, “Donge ma e ngʼat mane gidwaro nego cha?  
\v 26 To neuru koro opuonjo e lela, to onge ngʼama wachone gimoro. Koso dibed ni jodongwa oseyie ni en Kristo?  
\v 27 Wangʼeyo kuma ngʼatni oaye nikech Kristo to kobiro, to onge ngʼama nongʼe kuma oaye.” 
\p  
\v 28 Kane oyudo Yesu pod puonjo ei laru mar hekalu, nokok matek kowacho niya, \wj “Ee, ungʼeya, kendo ungʼeyo kuma aaye. Ok an ka gi dwarona awuon, to Jal ma noora en ja-adiera. Un ukiaye,\wj* 
\v 29 \wj to an to angʼeye nikech ne aa ire, kendo en ema noora.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 30 Kane giwinjo mano, ne gitemo mondo gimake, to onge ngʼama notemo mule gi lwete, nikech kindene ne pok ochopo.  
\v 31 Ji mathoth e dier ogandano pod noyie mana kuome. Negiwacho niya, “Ka Kristo miwachono obiro, bende notim honni mangʼeny moloyo ngʼatni adier?” 
\p  
\v 32 Jo-Farisai nowinjo ka oganda wacho gik ma kamago kuome, omiyo jodolo madongo gi jo-Farisai nooro askeche mag hekalu mondo omake. 
\p  
\v 33 Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “An kodu mana kuom kinde matin kende, bangʼe to abiro dok ir Jal mane oora.\wj* 
\v 34 \wj Ubiro manya, to ok unuyuda, kendo kama antie ok unyal bire.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 35 Jo-Yahudi nowacho e kindgi giwegi niya, “Ngʼatni dwadhi kune ma ok wanyal yudee? Dibed ni odwaro dhi kuma jowa odakie ka gikere e dier jo-Yunani mondo opuonj jo-Yunani?  
\v 36 Tiend gima nowacho ni, \wj ‘Ubiro manya to ok unuyuda’\wj* kendo ni, \wj ‘kama antie ok unyal bire’\wj* en angʼo?” 
\p  
\v 37 Odiechiengʼ mogik mar Sawo, mane en odiechiengʼ maduongʼ ahinya, Yesu nochungʼ mowacho gi dwol maduongʼ niya, \wj “Ngʼat ma riyo oloyo mondo obi ira omodhi.\wj* 
\v 38 \wj Ngʼato angʼata moyie kuoma pi ngima nobubni koa kuome, mana kaka Ndiko owacho.”\wj* 
\v 39 Gima ne owuoyo kuome ne en Roho, mane joma oyie kuome biro yudo bangʼe. E kindeno Roho ne pok obiro, nikech Yesu ne pok omi duongʼ. 
\p  
\v 40 Kane giwinjo wachno, moko kuom joma ne ni kanyo nowacho niya, “Jalni en janabi adier.” 
\p  
\v 41 Jomoko to nowacho niya, “En e Kristo.” 
\p Ji mamoko to nopenjo niya, “Ere kaka Kristo nyalo aa Galili?  
\v 42 Donge Ndiko wacho ni Kristo biro aa e anywola joka Daudi, kendo ni obiro aa Bethlehem, dala mane Daudi odakie?”  
\v 43 Omiyo pogruok nobedo e kind ji nikech wach Yesu.  
\v 44 Jomoko ne dwaro make, to onge ngʼama noketo lwete kuome. 
\s1 Jotend jo-Yahudi otamore yie kuom Yesu 
\p  
\v 45 Eka askeche mag hekalu nodok ir jodolo madongo gi jo-Farisai, kendo ne gipenjogi niya, “Angʼo momiyo ok usekele ka?” 
\p  
\v 46 Askeche nodwoko niya, “Onge ngʼama osewuoyo kaka ngʼatni nyaka nene.” 
\p  
\v 47 Jo-Farisai nodwokogi niya, “Kare un bende useyie gi miriambone.  
\v 48 Bende useneno jotend jo-Farisai kata achiel moyie kuome?  
\v 49 Onge ngʼama luwo ngʼatni makmana oganda mokia chik, gin joma okwongʼ!” 
\p  
\v 50 Nikodemo, jal manoyudo osedhi ir Yesu motelo, kendo mane en achiel kuomgi, nopenjo niya,  
\v 51 “Bende chikwa oyie adier mondo ongʼad ne ngʼato bura kapok onone mokwongo mondo ongʼe gima otimo?” 
\p  
\v 52 Negidwoke niya, “Donge in bende ia Galili? Non maber, to ibiro yudo ni onge janabi manyalo aa Galili.” 
\iex [Loko moko machon mag Muma kata joneno moko machon ne ok ondiko \xt Joh 7:53–8:11\xt*.] 
\p [ 
\v 53 Eka moro ka moro kuomgi nowuok modok e dalane. 
\c 8  
\nb  
\v 1 Yesu nodhi e Got Zeituni. 
\p  
\v 2 Kinyne gokinyi nochak odok e hekalu, kama ji duto nochokore kolwore, kendo nobet piny mopuonjogi.  
\v 3 Jopuonj Chik kod jo-Farisai nokelo dhako moro mane onwangʼ ka terore. Negikete ochungʼ e nyim joma ne ni kanyo duto,  
\v 4 bangʼe negiwachone Yesu niya, “Japuonj, dhakoni nende omaki rando ka terore.  
\v 5 Musa to nomiyowa chik mondo wachiel mon ma kamago gi kite. In to iwacho angʼo kuom wachni?”  
\v 6 Negiketo wachno e nyim Yesu mondo gigajego kendo giyud yo mane ginyalo donjonego. 
\p Yesu to nokulore piny kendo nochako ndiko e lowo gi lith lwete.  
\v 7 Kane gimedo dhi nyime gipenje, noa malo mowachonegi niya, \wj “Ngʼato kuomu mapok otimo richo ema okuong goye gi kidi.”\wj* 
\v 8 Eka nochako okulore piny mondiko e lowo. 
\p  
\v 9 Gikanyono, joma nowinjo gima nowachono nochako wuok achiel kaachiel, chakre jomadongo nyaka nyithindo mi dhakono ema nodongʼ kende kochungʼ but Yesu.  
\v 10 Yesu noa malo kendo nopenje niya, \wj “Nyarwa, eregi? Onge ngʼama odongʼ ma pod donjoni?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 11 Nowacho niya, “Jaduongʼ, onge ngʼat modongʼ.” 
\p Yesu nokone niya, \wj “Kata an bende ok angʼadni bura. Wuogi idhi, to kik ichak itim richo kendo.”\wj*] 
\s1 Gimomiyo nend Yesu en adier 
\p  
\v 12 Yesu nochako owuoyo kodgi, kowacho niya, \wj “An e ler mar piny, ngʼato angʼata ma luwa ok nyal wuotho e mudho, to enobed gi ler mar ngima.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 13 Omiyo jo-Farisai nokwede kagiwacho niya, “Itimo mana nendi iwuon, omiyo ok wanyal yie ni gik miwacho gin adier.” 
\p  
\v 14 Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Kata obedo ni atimo nenda awuon to nenda pod en mana adier nimar angʼeyo kuma ne aaye gi kuma adhiye. Un to ukia kuma aaye kata kuma adhiye.\wj* 
\v 15 \wj Ungʼado bura gi rieko mar dhano, an to ok angʼad bura ni ngʼato.\wj* 
\v 16 \wj To ka angʼado bura to paro ma angʼadogo bura nikare nikech ok atime kenda, to atime gi paro mar Wuoro mane oora.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Ondiki e chiku ni nend ji ariyo nyalo bedo adiera mi yiego.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj An atimo nenda awuon, to ngʼama chielo matimo nenda en Wuoro mane oora.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 19 Eka negipenje niya, “Wuonuno nikanye?” Yesu nodwokogi niya, 
\p \wj “Ukiaya kendo Wuora bende ukia. Ka dine bed ni ungʼeya, to Wuora bende dine ungʼeyo.”\wj* 
\v 20 Ne owacho wechegi kane oyudo opuonjo e laru mar hekalu, but kama ji ne ketoe sadaka. To onge ngʼama nomake, nikech kindene ne pok ochopo. 
\p  
\v 21 Yesu nowachonegi kendo niya, \wj “Abiro dhi aweyou, kendo ubiro manya, to unutho mana e richou. Kuma adhiye ok unyal bire.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 22 Wachneno nomiyo jo-Yahudi openjore niya, “Dibed ni ngʼatni dwaro dere? Dipo mano emomiyo owacho ni, \wj ‘Kuma adhiye ok unyal bire?’\wj* ” 
\p  
\v 23 To nomedo wachonegi niya, \wj “Unua mwalo e piny, an to aa malo e polo. Un jopinyni, to an ok an japinyni.\wj* 
\v 24 \wj Ne asenyisou ni ubiro tho e richou. Ka utamoru yie ni an ngʼama asebedo ka awachonu ni an, to ubiro tho e richou adier.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 25 Negipenje niya, “In ngʼa?” 
\p Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “An mana ngʼama asebedo ka awacho ni an nyaka aa chakruok.\wj* 
\v 26 \wj An gi gik mangʼeny monego awachnu mondo angʼadnugo bura. To Jal mane oora en ja-adiera, kendo anyiso piny gik ma asewinjo kuome.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 27 \wj Ne ok gingʼeyo ni ne owuoyonegi kuom Wuoro.\wj* 
\v 28 Omiyo Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “Bangʼ ka useguro Wuod Dhano eka unungʼe ni an ngʼama asebedo ka anyisou ni an, kendo ni onge gima atimo kenda, to awacho mana gik ma Wuora opuonja.\wj* 
\v 29 \wj Jal mane oora ni koda kendo pok oweya kenda, nimar atimo gik malongʼone kinde duto.”\wj* 
\v 30 Ji mangʼeny noyie kuome seche ma nowuoyono. 
\s1 Nyikwa Ibrahim 
\p  
\v 31 Yesu nowacho ni jo-Yahudi manoyie kuome niya, \wj “Ka usiko kumako puonjna, eka un jopuonjrena adier.\wj* 
\v 32 \wj Kutimo kamano, to ubiro ngʼeyo adiera kendo adiera nomi ubed thuolo.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 33 To negidwoke niya, “Wan koth Ibrahim kendo pok ne wabedo wasumb ngʼato nyaka nene. Ere gima omiyo iwachonwa ni ibiro miyowa wabed thuolo.” 
\p  
\v 34 Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Awachonu adier, ni ngʼato ka ngʼato matimo richo, en misumba richo.\wj* 
\v 35 \wj To ongʼere ni misumba ok luong ni wuod dala, to wuod wuon dala ema iluongo kamano nyaka chiengʼ.\wj* 
\v 36 \wj Omiyo ka Wuowi ema omiyo ubedo thuolo, to ubiro bedo thuolo chutho.\wj* 
\v 37 \wj Angʼeyo ni un koth Ibrahim, kata kamano udwaro nega, nikech udagi miyo Wachna thuolo e chunyu.\wj* 
\v 38 \wj An awachonu gik ma aseneno kuom Wuora wangʼ gi wangʼ, to un usiko utimo mana gik ma useneno kuom wuonu.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 39 Negidwoke niya, “Wan Ibrahim e Wuonwa.” 
\p Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “Ka dine bed ni un nyithind Ibrahim adier, to dine utimo gik ma Ibrahim notimo;\wj* 
\v 40 \wj to kar timo kamano to udwaro mana nega nikech asebedo kanyiso weche mag adiera mane Nyasaye omiya. Ibrahim to ne ok otimo gik ma kamago.\wj* 
\v 41 \wj Un timbe wuonu ema utimo.”\wj* 
\p Ne gikone ka gikwere niya, “Wan ok wan kimirwa. Wuoro ma wan-go en Nyasaye owuon.” 
\s1 Nyithind Satan 
\p  
\v 42 Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “Ka dine bed ni Nyasaye en Wuoru, dine uhera, nimar ne aa ir Nyasaye kendo koro an ka, ok asebiro kenda awuon, to en ema noora.\wj* 
\v 43 \wj Angʼo momiyo gik mawacho ok nyal donjonu kendo ok unyal winjo tiendgi?\wj* 
\v 44 \wj Un nyithind wuonu ma Satan kendo dwach wuonuno ema uhero timo. Ne en janek nyaka aa chakruok, kendo ok odwar adiera nikech adiera onge kuome. Koriambo to otimo gima ongʼiyogo, nimar en ja-miriambo, kendo en e wuon miriambo duto.\wj* 
\v 45 \wj To an ok uyie kuoma nikech awacho adiera!\wj* 
\v 46 \wj Ere ngʼato kuomu ka manyalo ngʼengʼa ni an jaricho? To ka awachonu adier to angʼo momiyo udagi yie kuoma?\wj* 
\v 47 \wj Ngʼat Nyasaye winjo weche Nyasaye, to un ok uwinj wach Nyasaye nikech ok un joge.”\wj* 
\s1 Gik ma Yesu nowacho kuome owuon 
\p  
\v 48 Jo-Yahudi nodwoke niya, “Donge wan kare ka wawacho ni in ja-Samaria kendo ni in gi jachien?” 
\p  
\v 49 Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Aonge gi jachien. Wuora ema amiyo duongʼ to un to uchaya.\wj* 
\v 50 \wj An ok adwar mondo umiya duongʼ, to nitie Jal machielo madwaro mondo ayud duongʼ, kendo en e jangʼad bura.\wj* 
\v 51 \wj Awachonu adier ni ka ngʼato orito wachna, to ok notho nyaka chiengʼ.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 52 Kane jo-Yahudi owinjo wachno, negiwachone niya, “Koro wangʼeyo maonge kiawa ni in gi jachien! Ibrahim notho, kendo jonabi bende notho, to in to iwacho ni ka ngʼato orito wachni to ok notho.  
\v 53 Iparo ni iduongʼ moloyo kwarwa Ibrahim? Ka en notho, to jonabi bende notho, in to iparo ni in ngʼa?” 
\p  
\v 54 Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Ka dipo ni amiyora duongʼ kenda, to duongʼna onge tich. Wuora, ma un bende uluongo ni Nyasachuno ema miya duongʼ.\wj* 
\v 55 \wj Kata obedo ni ok ungʼeye, anto angʼeye. Ka anyalo wacho ni ok angʼeye, to anyalo bedo ja-miriambo mana ka un, to angʼeye adier kendo pile angʼeyo wachne.\wj* 
\v 56 \wj Ibrahim kwaru ne mor koneno ndalona; adier, nonene mobedo mamor.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 57 Jo-Yahudi nowachone niya, “Pok ichopo kata higni piero abich, to Ibrahim to iseneno kanye!” 
\p  
\v 58 Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “Awachonu adier ni kane pok onywol Ibrahim, to ne Antie!”\wj* 
\v 59 Gikanyono ne gikwanyo kite mondo gichielgo Yesu, to nopondonigi, mopusore oa e laru mar hekalu. 
\c 9  
\s1 Yesu ochango ngʼat ma muofu 
\p  
\v 1 Kane oyudo owuotho odhi, noneno ngʼat moro mane osebedo muofu nyaka aa nywolne.  
\v 2 Jopuonjre nopenje niya, “Rabi, en ngʼa ma notimo richo; ngʼatni koso jonywolne, momiyo nonywole muofu?” 
\p  
\v 3 Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Ngʼatni kata jonywolne ne ok otimo richo, to ma notimore mondo teko mar Nyasaye onenre e changne.\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Nyaka wati tije mag Jal mane oora ka pod piny odiechiengʼ, nikech otieno biro maonge ngʼama nyalo tiyo.\wj* 
\v 5 \wj Ka pod an e piny, to an e ler mar piny.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 6 Kane osewacho kamano, nongʼudho olawo piny, mi olosogo chwodho, kaeto oketo e wangʼ ngʼatno.  
\v 7 Eka nowachone ngʼatno niya, \wj “Dhiyo ilwok wangʼi e yawo mar Siloam”\wj* (tiende ni “Ote”). Omiyo ngʼatno nodhi moluoko wangʼe, kendo noduogo dala koneno. 
\p  
\v 8 Jogwengʼ-gi gi joma nosenene motelo kokwecho nopenjo niya, “Donge ma e ngʼat mosebedo kakwechocha?”  
\v 9 Jomoko kuomgi nowacho ni mano en. 
\p Ji mamoko to nowacho niya, “Ooyo, ngʼatni chal mana kode.” 
\p Ngʼatno owuon to nowacho koramo niya, “En mana an.” 
\p  
\v 10 Negimedo penje niya, “Ka en kamano, to wengeni nokelo yawore nade?” 
\p  
\v 11 Nodwokogi niya, “Ngʼat miluongo ni Yesu noloso chwodho moro bangʼe oketo chwodhono e wengena. Nonyisa ni adhi Siloam aluok wangʼa, kendo ne adhi mi aluoko wangʼa, bangʼe ne aneno.” 
\p  
\v 12 Negipenje niya, “Ere ngʼatno?” 
\p To nodwokogi niya, “Ok angʼeyo kuma entiere.” 
\s1 Jo-Farisai onono kaka muofuni okelo chango 
\p  
\v 13 Ne gitero ngʼat machon ne muofuno ir jo-Farisai.  
\v 14 To chiengʼ mane Yesu olose chwodho kendo ochango wangʼ muofuno ne en chiengʼ Sabato.  
\v 15 Omiyo jo-Farisai nopenje kaka nokelo neno. To ngʼatno nodwokogi niya, “Nende oketo chwodho e wengena, bangʼe aluoko mi koro aneno.” 
\p  
\v 16 Moko kuom jo-Farisaigo nowacho niya, “Ngʼatni ok oa kuom Nyasaye, nimar ok orito Sabato.” 
\p Ji mamoko to nopenjo niya, “Ere kaka ngʼama jaricho nyalo timo tim hono machal kama?” Omiyo ne gipogore e kindgi giwegi. 
\p  
\v 17 Eka negichako gidonjore gi muofuno, mi gipenje niya, “In manende ochangi, to iwacho angʼo kuome?” 
\p Ngʼatno nodwokogi niya, “En janabi.” 
\p  
\v 18 To jo-Yahudi ne pod ok oyie ni ngʼatni nonywol ka en muofu, kendo ni wengene noseyawore, nyaka negioro wach mondo oluong jonywol ngʼatno.  
\v 19 Ne gipenjogi niya, “Bende ngʼatni e wuodu ma uwacho ni nonywol muofu? Obet nade ni koro onyalo neno?” 
\p  
\v 20 Jonywolgo nodwokogi niya, “Wangʼeyo ni ma en wuodwa, kendo wangʼeyo ni nonywole muofu.  
\v 21 To kaka koro onyalo neno sani, kata ngʼama noyawo wengene, to wakia. Penjeuru, tinde oduongʼ. Obiro wacho wach kuome owuon.”  
\v 22 Jonywolne nowacho kamano nikech negiluoro jo-Yahudi, nimar noyudo jo-Yahudi osengʼado wach ni ngʼato angʼata ma nohul ni Yesu en Kristo ne ibiro riembi e sinagogi.  
\v 23 Mano emomiyo jonywolne nowacho niya, “Tinde oduongʼ, penjeuru.” 
\p  
\v 24 Negichako giluongo ngʼat ma nonywol ka en muofuno mi gikone niya, “Wach adier e nyim Nyasaye! Wan wangʼeyo ni ngʼatni en jaricho.” 
\p  
\v 25 Nodwokogi niya, “An akia kata ka en jaricho kata ka ok en. Gimoro achiel kende ema angʼeyo: Ni chon ne an muofu, to sani koro aneno!” 
\p  
\v 26 Eka negipenje niya, “Angʼo ma notimoni ma wangʼi oneno? Ere kaka noyawo wengeni?” 
\p  
\v 27 Nodwokogi niya, “Donge ne asenyisou, to ok uyie. Udwaro winje kendo nangʼo? Koso un bende udwaro doko jopuonjrene?” 
\p  
\v 28 Kuom mano, ne giyanye mangʼeny kagiwacho niya, “In e japuonjrene! Wan to wan jopuonjre Musa.  
\v 29 Wangʼeyo ni Nyasaye nowuoyo gi Musa, to ngʼatni to wakia kata mana kuma oaye.” 
\p  
\v 30 Ngʼatno nodwokogi niya, “Mano en wach miwuoro! Ukia kuma oaye to en ema noyawo wengena?  
\v 31 Wangʼeyo ni Nyasaye ok winj jaricho. Owinjo mana ngʼatno matimo dwarone.  
\v 32 Nyaka nene pok nowinji ngʼat moyawo wangʼ ngʼat mane onywol ka en muofu.  
\v 33 Ka dine bed ni ngʼatni ok noa kuom Nyasaye, to ok dine otimo gimoro.” 
\p  
\v 34 Omiyo negidwoke niya, “In nonywoli e chuny richo, koro ere kaka inyalo bukori ni ipuonjowa!” Bangʼ mano negiriembe oko. 
\s1 Bedo muofu kuom Wach Nyasaye 
\p  
\v 35 Yesu nowinjo ni ne oseriemb ngʼatno oko, omiyo kane oyude, nopenje niya, \wj “Bende iyie kuom Wuod Dhano?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 36 Ngʼatno nopenjo niya, “Jaduongʼ, Wuod Dhano to en ngʼa? Nyisago mondo ayie kuome.” 
\p  
\v 37 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Eri koro isenene; kendo en ema owuoyo kodini.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 38 Ngʼatno nowachone niya, “Ruoth, ayie,” kendo nolame. 
\p  
\v 39 Eka Yesu nowacho niya, \wj “Asebiro e piny mondo angʼadne bura, mondo joma muofni onen, to joma neno olokre muofni.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 40 Jo-Farisai moko mane ni kode nowinje kowacho kamano mi openje niya, “Iwacho angʼono? Kare wan bende wan muofni?” 
\p  
\v 41 Yesu nowachonegi niya, “Ka dine bed ni un muofni, to dine ok ubedo joketho nikech richo; to nikech uketoru ni uneno, koro kethou osiko.” 
\c 10  
\s1 Jakwath kod rombe 
\p  
\v 1 Yesu nomedo wachonegi niya, \wj “Adier, adier, awachonu ni ngʼama ok donji e abich rombe koluwo dhorangach, to odonjo koluwo yo machielo, en jakuo kendo jamecho.\wj* 
\v 2 \wj Ngʼat madonjo koluwo dhorangach e jakwadh rombe.\wj* 
\v 3 \wj Jarito yawone dhorangach kendo rombe winjo dwonde. Oluongo rombene owuon gi nying-gi kendo otelonegi kagiwuok oko moro ka moro.\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Ka osegolo rombene duto oko, to otelo e nyimgi, kendo rombene luwo bangʼe nikech gingʼeyo kit dwonde.\wj* 
\v 5 \wj To ok ginyal luwo bangʼ ngʼama gikia. Adier, giringo gia bute nikech ok gingʼeyo dwonde.”\wj* 
\v 6 Yesu notiyo gi ngeroni to ne ok giwinjo tiend gima nonyisogi. 
\p  
\v 7 Kuom mano, Yesu nochako owachonegi niya, \wj “Adier, adier, awachonu ni an e dhoranga rombe.\wj* 
\v 8 \wj Ji duto mane obiro motelona ne gin jokwoge kendo jomecho, to rombe ne ok owinjogi.\wj* 
\v 9 \wj An e dhorangach; ma ngʼato angʼata mokadho kuoma nokwo kendo nodonj iye mi owuog oko kendo oyud kar kwath maber.\wj* 
\v 10 \wj Jakuo biro mana mondo okwal kendo oneki kendo oketh gik moko, An to asebiro mondo giyud ngima, kendo giyude mogundho.\wj* 
\p  
\v 11 \wj “An e jakwath maber. Jakwath maber chiwo ngimane ne rombe.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Jatij ngʼato ok en jakwath ma wuon rombe. Omiyo koneno ondiek kabiro, to oringo oweyo rombe kanyo. Eka ondiek monjo rombe kendo keyogi.\wj* 
\v 13 \wj Ngʼatno ringo tony nikech en mana jatich kendo ngima rombe ok obadhe.\wj* 
\p  
\v 14 \wj “An e jakwath maber; angʼeyo rombena kendo rombena bende ongʼeya.\wj* 
\v 15 \wj Gingʼeya mana kaka Wuora ongʼeya kendo angʼeyo Wuoro, kendo achiwo ngimana ne rombe.\wj* 
\v 16 \wj An gi rombe moko ma ok ni e abich rombegi. Gin bende nyaka akelgi kendo giniwinj dwonda, eka rombe duto nobed kweth achiel man-gi jakwath achiel.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Gimomiyo Wuora ohera en nikech ayie chiwo ngimana, eka achako akawe kendo.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Onge ngʼama nyalo kawe kuoma, to achiwe nikech ahero. An gi teko mar chiwe bende an gi teko mar kawe kendo. Tekoni ne ayudo kuom Wuora.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 19 Wechegi nomedo kelo pogruok e kind jo-Yahudi.  
\v 20 Ji mangʼeny nowacho niya, “Ngʼatni nigi jachien kendo ojaneko, en angʼo momiyo uchiko itu ni wechene?” 
\p  
\v 21 Ji mamoko to nowacho niya, “Magi ok gin weche ma ngʼama nigi jachien nyalo wacho. Jachien bende nyalo yawo wangʼ muofu adier?” 
\s1 Tamruok yie mar jo-Yahudi 
\p  
\v 22 Eka kinde mar Sawo mar Puodho hekalu nochopo Jerusalem. Ne en ndalo chwiri  
\v 23 kendo noyudo Yesu nitie machiegni gi hekalu, kowuotho e agola mar Solomon.  
\v 24 Jo-Yahudi nochokore molwore, kendo negiwachone niya, “Pod ibiro weyowa e mudho nyaka karangʼo? Ka in e Kristo to nyiswa maler.” 
\p  
\v 25 Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Asenyisou, to utamoru yie. Honni ma atimo e nying Wuora bende nyiso gima An,\wj* 
\v 26 \wj to udagi yie nikech ok un rombena.\wj* 
\v 27 \wj Rombena winjo dwonda, bende angʼeyogi kendo giluwo bangʼa.\wj* 
\v 28 \wj Amiyogi ngima mochwere, kendo ok ginilal ngangʼ, bende onge ngʼama nyalo kawogi kagologi e lweta.\wj* 
\v 29 \wj Wuora mosemiyagi duongʼ moloyo duto, kendo onge ngʼama nyalo kawogi mi golgi e lwet Wuora.\wj* 
\v 30 \wj An kod Wuora wan achiel.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 31 Kane jo-Yahudi owinjo wachno, negichako gikwanyo kite mondo gichielego,  
\v 32 to Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “Asenyisou honni madongo mangʼeny moa ka Wuora. Kuom honnigi duto, en mane kuomgi ma udwaro chielane gi kite?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 33 Jo-Yahudi nodwoke niya, “Ok wachieli gi kite nikech honni madongo misetimo, to wachieli gi kite nikech iseyanyo Nyasaye. In mana dhano adhanani, ere kaka inyalo ketori ni in Nyasaye?” 
\p  
\v 34 Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Donge ondiki e chiku ni, ‘Ne awacho ni un “nyiseche” ’\wj*\f + \fr 10:34 \ft \xt Zab 82:6\f*\wj ?\wj* 
\v 35 \wj Kane oluongo joma wach Nyasaye nobironigi ni ‘nyiseche,’ to ongʼere ni Ndiko ok nyal kethi,\wj* 
\v 36 \wj to koro unyalo wacho angʼo kuom Jal ma Wuoro nowalo kaka Ngʼate owuon mi ooro e piny? Ka kamano, to angʼo momiyo udonjona gi ketho mar yanyo Nyasaye, nikech nende awacho ni, ‘An Wuod Nyasaye’?\wj* 
\v 37 \wj Ka dipo ni ok atim gik ma Wuora timo, to kik uyie kuoma.\wj* 
\v 38 \wj To ka atimogi, to yieuru kuom honnigo, kata ka an ok udwar yie kuoma, mondo ungʼe maber ni Wuoro ni e iya kendo an ei Wuoro.”\wj* 
\v 39 Ne gitemo make kendo, to nopusore e lwetgi. 
\p  
\v 40 Eka Yesu nongʼado Jordan modok kama Johana ne batisoe ji kinde motelo. Nodak kanyo,  
\v 41 kendo ji mangʼeny nobiro ire. Negiwacho niya, “Kata obedo ni Johana ne ok otimo tim hono moro amora, to gik moko duto manowacho kuom ngʼatni ne gin adier.”  
\v 42 Kamano, ji mangʼeny noyie kuom Yesu kanyo. 
\c 11  
\s1 Tho mar Lazaro 
\p  
\v 1 Ngʼat moro ma nyinge Lazaro ne tuo. Ne en ja-Bethania, dala gi Maria gi Maritha nyamin mare.  
\v 2 Maria-ni ma owadgi Lazaro makoro tuoni ema noolo mo mangʼwe ngʼar e tiend Ruoth mi oyweyo gi yie wiye.  
\v 3 Omiyo nyimine Lazaro nooro wach ni Yesu niya, “Ruoth, osiepni mihero tuo.” 
\p  
\v 4 Kane Yesu owinjo mano, nowacho niya, \wj “Tuono ok en mar tho, to mano otimore mana ni mondo Nyasaye oyud duongʼ, kendo mondo Wuod Nyasaye oyud duongʼ kuome.”\wj* 
\v 5 Yesu nohero Maritha gi nyamin mare kod Lazaro.  
\v 6 To kata kamano, kane owinjo ni Lazaro tuo, nomedo bedo kama ne entie kuom ndalo ariyo. 
\p  
\v 7 Eka nowacho ni jopuonjrene niya, \wj “Wadoguru Judea.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 8 To jopuonjrene nodwoke niya, “Rabi, ere kaka didog kuno to nyocha eka jo-Yahudi dwaro goyi gi kite?” 
\p  
\v 9 Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Donge nitie seche apar gariyo e odiechiengʼ? Ngʼat mawuotho godiechiengʼ ok chwanyre, nimar ler mar piny miyo oneno.\wj* 
\v 10 \wj Kowuotho gotieno eka ochwanyore, nikech oonge gi ler.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 11 Bangʼ kane osewacho kamano, nomedo loso kodgi kowacho niya, \wj “Osiepwa ma Lazaro nindo osetero, to adwaro dhi kuno mondo achiewe.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 12 Jopuonjrene nodwoke niya, “Ruoth, konindo aninda, to obiro mana chiewo.”  
\v 13 Yesu ne wuoyo kuom tho Lazaro, to jopuonjrene to ne paro ni oloso mana kuom nindo mapile. 
\p  
\v 14 Omiyo koro nonyisogi ratiro niya, \wj “Lazaro otho,\wj* 
\v 15 \wj to amor ni nyocha otho ka aonge kuno, mondo eka uyie. Kata kamano, wawuog wadhiuru ire.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 16 Eka Thoma, ma bende iluongo ni Didimas, nowachone jopuonjre mamoko niya, “Wan bende wadhiuru mondo kata ka en tho, to watho kode.” 
\s1 Yesu ohoyo Maritha gi Maria 
\p  
\v 17 Kane Yesu ochopo, to noyudo ka Lazaro osetieko ndalo angʼwen e bur.  
\v 18 Bethania ne chiegni gi Jerusalem madirom kar kilomita adek,  
\v 19 kendo jo-Yahudi mangʼeny noyudo osebiro ir Maritha gi Maria mondo ohogi e kuyo margi kuom tho mar owadgi.  
\v 20 Kane Maritha owinjo ni Yesu biro, nowuok oko mondo oromne, ka Maria to nodongʼ ei ot. 
\p  
\v 21 Maritha nowacho ni Yesu niya, “Ruoth, ka dinyocha bed ni in ka, to owadwa dine ok otho.  
\v 22 To angʼeyo ni kata mana sani Nyasaye biro miyi gimoro amora mikwaye.” 
\p  
\v 23 Yesu nowachone niya, \wj “Owadu biro chier.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 24 Maritha nodwoke niya, “Angʼeyo ni obiro chier kendo e ndalo chier, ma en chiengʼ giko piny.” 
\p  
\v 25 Yesu nowachone niya, \wj “An e chier kendo An e ngima. Ngʼat moyie kuoma kata otho to nodok mangima,\wj* 
\v 26 \wj kendo ngʼama ngima moyie kuoma ok notho ngangʼ. Bende iyie gi wachni?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 27 Eka nodwoke niya, “Ee, Ruoth, ayie ni in e Kristo ma Wuod Nyasaye, ma nonego obi e piny.” 
\p  
\v 28 Kane osewacho mano, to nodok oluongo Maria nyamin-gi tenge, mowachone niya, “Japuonj nika, kendo oluongi.”  
\v 29 Kane Maria owinjo mano, noa malo piyo piyo mi odhi ire.  
\v 30 Noyudo Yesu pok odonjo ei dalano; to ne pod ochungʼ oko kama Maritha noromonee.  
\v 31 Ka jo-Yahudi manoyudo nigi Maria ei ot, kahoye, nonene kochungʼ girikni modhi oko, negiluwo bangʼe, ka giparo ni odhi e liel mondo oywagi kuno. 
\p  
\v 32 Kane Maria ochopo kama Yesu ne nitie monene gi wangʼe, nopodho e tiende mowachone niya, “Ruoth, ka dinyocha bed ni in ka to owadwa dine ok otho.” 
\p  
\v 33 Kane Yesu onene koywak, kendo ka jo-Yahudi mane gibirogo ire bende ne ywak, chunye nodoko malit kendo nochandore.  
\v 34 Nopenjo niya, \wj “Ne uiko ringre kanye?”\wj* 
\p Negidwoke niya, “Ruoth, bi wadhi wanyisi.” 
\p  
\v 35 Pi wangʼ Yesu nochwer. 
\p  
\v 36 Eka jo-Yahudi nowacho niya, “Neyeuru kaka nohere!” 
\p  
\v 37 Ji moko kuomgi to nopenjore niya, “Jal ma yande oyawo wangʼ muofuni, donge nyocha onyalo gengʼo tho Lazaro?” 
\s1 Yesu ochiero Lazaro 
\p  
\v 38 Yesu nochopo kar liel ka chunye nigi kuyo maduongʼ moloyo. Ne en rogo, kendo noyie kidi e dhoge.  
\v 39 Yesu nowacho niya, \wj “Goluru kidino oko e dho liel.”\wj* 
\p To Maritha ma nyamin ngʼat mane othono nokwer niya, “Ruoth, sani koro en gi tik marach, nimar osetieko ndalo angʼwen nyaka notho.” 
\p  
\v 40 Yesu nowachone niya, \wj “Donge nende anyisi ni kiyie to ibiro neno duongʼ mar Nyasaye?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 41 Omiyo ne gingʼielo kidino oko. Eka Yesu nongʼiyo malo mowacho niya, \wj “Wuora, agoyoni erokamano nikech isewinja.\wj* 
\v 42 \wj Angʼeyo bende ni isebedo kiwinja ndalo duto, to asewacho wechegi mondo joma ochungʼ ka oyud konyruok, kendo mondo giyie nine iora adier.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 43 Bangʼ wacho mano, Yesu noluongo gi dwol maduongʼ niya, \wj “Lazaro, wuog oko!”\wj* 
\v 44 Mi ngʼama nothono nowuok oko, ka bedene gi tiendene onal gi lewni molir olir, kendo ka lela wangʼe bende otwe gi nanga alwora. 
\p Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “Gonyuru lep liel oko kuome mondo uweye odhi.”\wj* 
\s1 Jo-Yahudi ochano mar nego Yesu 
\p  
\v 45 Kuom mano, jo-Yahudi mangʼeny mane obiro hoyo chuny Maria, kendo ma noneno gima Yesu notimo, noyie kuome.  
\v 46 Ji moko kuomgi to nodhi ir jo-Farisai monyisogi gima Yesu nosetimo.  
\v 47 Eka jodolo madongo gi jo-Farisai nochoko buch jo-Sanhedrin, kendo negipenjore niya, 
\p “Watim angʼo? Ngʼatni medo timo timbe honni mangʼeny moloyo.  
\v 48 Ka waweye odhi nyime kama, to ji duto biro yie kuome, kendo kamano otimore to jo-Rumi biro biro mi kaw karwa ka, kaachiel gi pinywa bende.” 
\p  
\v 49 To achiel kuomgi, mane nyinge Kaifas, mane en jadolo maduongʼ e higano nowachonegi niya, “Un joma ok riek kata matin!  
\v 50 Ok unyal fwenyo ni en gima ber moloyo mondo ngʼato achiel otho ni ji duto, moloyo ka oganda duto otho.” 
\p  
\v 51 Ne ok owacho wachni gi pache owuon, to kaka ne en jadolo maduongʼ e higano, nokoro wach ni Yesu ne biro tho ne piny jo-Yahudi,  
\v 52 to ok ne pinyno kende, to ne nyithind Nyasaye duto mokere, mondo ochokgi kaachiel, kendo omi gibed gimoro achiel.  
\v 53 Omiyo chakre chiengʼno kadhi nyime negichano kaka ginyalo nego Yesu. 
\p  
\v 54 Kuom mano, Yesu koro ne ok wuothi e dier jo-Yahudi ka ji nene. Nopondo modhi e gwengʼ man but thim, e dala miluongo ni Efraim, kendo nobet kuno gi jopuonjrene. 
\p  
\v 55 Ka kinde mag Pasaka mar jo-Yahudi ne chiegni chopo, ji mangʼeny moa e gwenge mopogore opogore nodhi Jerusalem mondo gipwodhre kapok Pasaka ochopo.  
\v 56 Negisiko ka gimanyo Yesu, kendo negipenjore ngʼato gi ngʼato, ka gichungʼ ei alwora mar hekalu niya, “Uparo nade? Donge obiro biro e sawoni koso ok obi biro?”  
\v 57 Negiwacho kamano nikech jodolo madongo gi jo-Farisai ne osegolo chik ni ngʼato angʼata mongʼeyo kuma Yesu nitie nyaka ternegi wach mondo gidhi gimake. 
\c 12  
\s1 Maria owiro Yesu gi mo Bethania 
\p  
\v 1 Kane pod odongʼ ndalo auchiel mondo Pasaka ochopi, Yesu notundo Bethania, kama Lazaro nodakie, mane en ngʼat mane Yesu ochiero oa kuom joma otho.  
\v 2 Negiloso nyasi maduongʼ Bethania ne Yesu. Maritha ne miyo welo chiemo, to Lazaro to nobet kachiemo kaachiel gi joma nobet kolworo mesa.  
\v 3 Eka Maria nokawo mo mangʼwe ngʼar kendo ma nengone tek, manyalo romo nus lita, mowirogo tiende Yesu, bangʼe oyweyo tiendene gi yie wiye. Mi ot nopongʼ gi tik mangʼwe ngʼar mar mono. 
\p  
\v 4 Judas Iskariot, ma en achiel kuom jopuonjre Yesu kendo mane biro ndhoge bangʼe, nokwero tim mane dhakono otimo, kowacho niya,  
\v 5 “Angʼo ma nomone hono mo mangʼwe ngʼarno mondo pesa moyudi omi joma odhier? Onge tiende ketho mo ma nengone tek kama, moromo chulo misach ngʼat achiel kuom higa ngima.”  
\v 6 Ne ok owacho kamano nikech nohero jodhier, to nikech ne en jakuo. Kaka jakeno mar pesa, nothoro konyore gi pesa ma nokanogo. 
\p  
\v 7 Yesu nodwoko niya, \wj “Weyeuru mos. Ne ochan chon ni owinjore okan mo mangʼwe ngʼarno nyaka chiengʼ yikna.\wj* 
\v 8 \wj Joma odhier ubiro bedogo e dieru kinde duto, to an ok ubi siko koda ndalo duto.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 9 E kindeno, jo-Yahudi mangʼeny nofwenyo ni Yesu ne nitie kanyo mi negibiro, ok nikech en, to nikech negidwaro neno Lazaro, manoyudo osechiero oa kuom joma otho.  
\v 10 Omiyo jodolo madongo noloso chenro kaka digineg Lazaro kaachiel kode,  
\v 11 nimar wachne nomiyo jo-Yahudi mangʼeny koro ne weyogi dhi ir Yesu kendo giyie kuome. 
\s1 Yesu odonjo Jerusalem gi rwak maduongʼ 
\p  
\v 12 Kinyne, oganda maduongʼ mane oyudo obiro e Sawo nowinjo ni Yesu ni e yo biro Jerusalem.  
\v 13 Negikawo bede othidhe mi giwuok oko mondo giromne, ka gikok niya, 
\q1 “Hosana!” 
\b  
\q1 “Ogwedh ngʼat mabiro e nying Jehova Nyasaye!”\f + \fr 12:13 \ft \xt Zab 118:25,26\f* 
\b  
\q1 “Ogwedh Ruodh Israel!” 
\m  
\v 14 Yesu noyudo nyathi kanyna moro moidho obetie, mana kaka Ndiko wacho niya, 
\q1  
\v 15 “Kik ibed maluor, yaye Nyar Sayun; 
\q2 nee, ruodhi eri biro, 
\q2 koidho nyathi kanyna.”\f + \fr 12:15 \ft \xt Zek 9:9\f* 
\p  
\v 16 Mokwongo jopuonjrene ne ok owinjo tiend gigi duto, to achien, bangʼ ka Yesu nosemi duongʼ eka negifwenyo ni wechegi nosendiki kuome chon, kendo ni gigo notimore nikech en. 
\p  
\v 17 Oganda mane ni kode chiengʼ mane oluongo Lazaro oa e liel, ka nochiere oa kuom joma otho, nomedo lando wachno.  
\v 18 Omiyo ji mangʼeny nowuok mondo giromne, nikech negisewinjo ni en ema yande otimo honono.  
\v 19 Kuom mano, jo-Farisai nowacho e kindgi ngʼato gi ngʼato niya, “Uneno ka wachni e muomowa. Neyeuru kaka piny duto osewuok luwo bangʼe!” 
\s1 Yesu okoro thone 
\p  
\v 20 Koro ne nitie jo-Yunani moko kuom joma ne biro lemo e Sawono.  
\v 21 Negibiro ir Filipo, mane aa Bethsaida, e piny Galili, mi gikwaye niya, “Jaduongʼ, wadwaro neno Yesu.”  
\v 22 Filipo nodhi monyiso Andrea wachno; eka Andrea kod Filipo nodhi ir Yesu ma ginyise wachno. 
\p  
\v 23 Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Sa osechopo mondo Wuod Dhano omi duongʼ.\wj* 
\v 24 \wj Awachonu adier ni ka koth cham ok oiki e lowo motho, to osiko mana kodhi achiel kende. To ka otho, to onywolo kothe mangʼeny.\wj* 
\v 25 \wj Ngʼama ohero ngimane, ngimane biro lalne, to ngʼama ochayo ngimane e pinyni biro rite nyaka chop oyud ngima mochwere.\wj* 
\v 26 \wj Ngʼato angʼata matiyona nyaka luwa, kendo kama antie ema jatichna bende nobedie. Ngʼat matiyona Wuora biro miyo duongʼ.\wj* 
\p  
\v 27 \wj “Koro chunya chandore, to en angʼo ma dawachi? Dawach ni, ‘Wuora, resa e sa machalo kama?’ Ooyo, ok onyal timo kamano nikech ma e gima omiyo ne abiro e kindeni.\wj* 
\v 28 \wj Wuora, mi nyingi duongʼ!”\wj* 
\p Eka dwol moro noa e polo, kawacho niya, “Asemiye duongʼ kendo abiro chako amiye duongʼ.”  
\v 29 Oganda mane ni kanyo manowinjo dwolno nowacho ni polo ema nomor, to ji mamoko to nowacho ni malaika ema nowuoyo kode. 
\p  
\v 30 Yesu nokonegi niya, \wj “Dwolno ne ok obiro mondo okonya, to nobiro mondo okonyu.\wj* 
\v 31 \wj Koro sa osechopo ma ingʼadone piny bura, kendo sani ema ruodh pinyni noriemb oko.\wj* 
\v 32 \wj To an, bangʼ kosetingʼa malo mogola e pinyni, to anaywa ji duto ira.”\wj* 
\v 33 Nowacho mano mondo onyisgo kit tho ma nobiro thogo. 
\p  
\v 34 Ogandano nodwoke niya, “Wasewinjo e chik ni Kristo biro siko nyaka chiengʼ, ka en kamano, to ikelo wacho nade ni, ‘\wj Wuod Dhano nyaka bi tingʼ malo’\wj*? ‘Wuod Dhano’ miwuoyo kuomeno to en ngʼa?” 
\p  
\v 35 Eka Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Pod ubiro bedo gi ler kuom ndalo manok. Wuothuru kapod un gi ler; ka mudho pok ojukou. Ngʼama wuotho e mudho okia kuma odhiye.\wj* 
\v 36 \wj Keturu genou kuom ler kapod un kode, mondo mi ubed nyithind ler.”\wj* Kane Yesu osetieko wuoyo kodgi, to nowuok owegi kendo nopondonigi. 
\s1 Jo-Yahudi otamore yie kuom Yesu 
\p  
\v 37 To kata obedo ni Yesu nosetimo honnigo duto ka gineno gi wengegi, to pod ne gidagi mana yie kuome.  
\v 38 Mano notimore mondo ochop wach mane Isaya janabi osewacho niya, 
\q1 “Jehova Nyasaye, en ngʼa moseyie wach mwalando, 
\q2 koso en ngʼa ma Jehova Nyasaye osenyiso tekone?”\f + \fr 12:38 \ft \xt Isa 53:1\f* 
\p  
\v 39 Kuom mano, ne ok ginyal yie, mana kaka Isaya nowacho bende komachielo niya, 
\q1  
\v 40 “Osedino wengegi 
\q2 kendo osemiyo chunygi odoko matek, 
\q1 mondo kik gine gimoro gi wengegi, 
\q2 kendo kik giwinj tiend weche gi chunygi, 
\q2 mi gilokre gidwog ira mi achang-gi.”\f + \fr 12:40 \ft \xt Isa 6:10\f* 
\m  
\v 41 Isaya nowacho kamano nikech noneno duongʼ maler mar Yesu kendo nowuoyo kuome. 
\p  
\v 42 Kata kamano, e kindeno, ji mangʼeny kuom jotelo bende noyie kuome. To nikech negiluoro jo-Farisai, ne ok ginyal hulo yie margi e lela nimar negiluor ni dipo ka oriembgi e sinagogi.  
\v 43 Nimar ne gihero pak moa kuom dhano moloyo pak moa kuom Nyasaye. 
\p  
\v 44 Eka Yesu nokok matek kawacho niya, \wj “Ka ngʼato oyie kuoma, to an ok ema oyie kuoma kenda, to oyie kuom Jal mane oora bende.\wj* 
\v 45 \wj Ngʼama nena, neno Jal mane oora.\wj* 
\v 46 \wj Asebiro e piny kaka ler, mondo ngʼato angʼata moyie kuoma kik sik e mudho.\wj* 
\p  
\v 47 \wj “To ngʼat mawinjo wechena to ok riti, to an ok angʼadne bura, nikech ne ok abiro mondo angʼadne piny bura, to nabiro mondo ares piny.\wj* 
\v 48 \wj Nitie Ngʼat mangʼado bura ne ngʼama odaga kendo ma ok oyie wechena. Ngʼama kamano wachna mane awacho ema biro ngʼadone bura marach chiengʼ giko piny.\wj* 
\v 49 \wj Nimar ne ok awuoyo gi dwacha awuon, to Wuoro ma noora ema nochika mondo awachi gik ma asebedo ka awacho kendo kaka onego awachgi.\wj* 
\v 50 \wj Angʼeyo ni chikne ema kelo ngima mochwere. Kuom mano, gimoro amora ma awacho en mana gima Wuora onyisa mondo awachi.”\wj* 
\c 13  
\s1 Yesu olwoko tiend jopuonjrene 
\p  
\v 1 Kane Sap Pasaka okayo machiegni, Yesu nongʼeyo ni sane osechopo mar wuok e pinyni mondo odog ir Wuoro. Kaka nosehero joge owuon mane ni e pinyni, koro noikore nyisogi herane matut mogik. 
\p  
\v 2 E kinde mane gichano chiemb odhiambo, noyudo Jachien oseketo paro marach e chuny Judas Iskariot, ma wuod Simon, mondo ondhog Yesu.  
\v 3 Yesu nongʼeyo ni Wuoro noseketo gik moko duto e bwo tekone, kendo ni noa ka Nyasaye kendo nobiro dok ir Nyasaye;  
\v 4 omiyo noa malo oweyo chiemo, kendo nongʼwano kandhone bangʼe otweyo taulo e nungone.  
\v 5 Bangʼ timo kamano, noolo pi e karaya bangʼe ochako luoko tiend jopuonjrene, kendo noyweyo tiendegi gi taulo mane oyudo otweyo e nungone. 
\p  
\v 6 Kane obiro ir Simon Petro, Petro nowachone niya, “Ruoth, idwaro luoko tienda adier?” 
\p  
\v 7 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Ok inyal winjo tiend gima atimo, to ibiro winjo tiende bangʼe.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 8 Petro nonyise koramo niya, “Ooyo, Ruoth, ok inyal luoko tiendena ngangʼ.” 
\p Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Ka ok aluoko tiendi, to ok iwinjori bedo koda e kanyakla mar jopuonjrena.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 9 Simon Petro nodwoke niya, “Ruoth, ka kamano, to kik ilwok mana tienda kende, to luok bedena kod wiya bende!” 
\p  
\v 10 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Ngʼat moseluokore onego olwok mana tiendene kende, nimar dende duto ler. Un usedoko maler, makmana ngʼato achiel kuomu kende ema ok ler.”\wj* 
\v 11 Nikech nongʼeyo ngʼat mane biro ndhoge, mano emomiyo nowachonegi ni ok giler giduto. 
\p  
\v 12 Kane osetieko luoko tiendegi, norieyo kandhone bangʼe nodok obet piny. Nopenjogi niya, \wj “Bende ungʼeyo tiend gima asetimonuno?\wj* 
\v 13 \wj Uluonga kare ni ‘Japuonj’ kendo ni ‘Ruoth,’ kendo utimo kare, nikech mano e ngʼama an.\wj* 
\v 14 \wj Koro ka an ma an Ruodhu kendo Japuonju ema aselwoko tiendeu, un bende nyaka ulwok tiendeu ngʼato gi ngʼato.\wj* 
\v 15 \wj Aseketonu ranyisi mondo utim kaka asetimonu.\wj* 
\v 16 \wj Awachonu adier ni onge jatich maduongʼ moloyo ruodhe motiyone, kata jaote ok duongʼ moloyo ngʼama oore.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Nikech koro ungʼeyo wechegi, nogwedhu kutiyo kodgi.”\wj* 
\s1 Yesu owuoyo kuom thone 
\p  
\v 18 \wj Yesu nomedo wuoyo kodgi niya, “Ok awuo kuomu un uduto, nimar angʼeyo joma aseyiero. To mano osetimore mondo ochop Ndiko mawacho ni, ‘Ngʼat machiemo koda bende osendhoga.’\wj*\f + \fr 13:18 \ft \xt Zab 41:9\f* 
\p  
\v 19 \wj “Koro anyisou wachni chon kapok otimore mondo kotimore, to ubiro yie ni An e Kristo.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj Awachonu adier, ni ngʼato angʼata morwako ngʼama aoro, orwaka, kendo ngʼama orwaka orwako jal ma noora.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 21 Bangʼ kane osewacho mano, Yesu nochandore gie chunye mi nohulonigi niya, \wj “Awachonu adier, ni achiel kuomu biro ndhoga.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 22 Jopuonjrene dhogi nomoko, kendo ne gingʼiyore kendgi ka giparo ni en ngʼa kuomgi ma nowuoyo kuome.  
\v 23 To noyudo japuonjre mane Yesu ohero, ne chiemo kobedo bute machiegni.  
\v 24 Simon Petro nogwelo japuonjreno kawacho niya, “Penje ane ngʼama owuoyo kuome.” 
\p  
\v 25 Nolokore motenore kuom Yesu mopenje niya, “Ruoth, en ngʼa?” 
\p  
\v 26 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “En ngʼama abiro miyo makatini bangʼ ka aselute e kado.”\wj* Eka, bangʼ luto makati e kado, nomiye Judas Iskariot wuod Simon.  
\v 27 To kane Judas osekawo makatino, Satan nodonjo kuome. 
\p Yesu nokone niya, \wj “Gima idwaro timono, tim piyo.”\wj* 
\v 28 To kuom joma ne chiemo kanyo, onge ngʼama nongʼeyo gimomiyo nowachone kamano.  
\v 29 To kaka Judas ne en jakeno mar pesa, jomoko ne paro ni Yesu nonyise mondo odhi ongʼiew gik mane dwarore e sawo, kata ni mondo ochiw gimoro ni jodhier.  
\v 30 Mapiyo bangʼ ka Judas nosekawo makatino, nowuok oweyogi. Koro ne en seche mag otieno. 
\s1 Yesu okoro ni Petro biro kwede 
\p  
\v 31 Kane Judas osedhi, Yesu nowacho niya, \wj “Wuod Dhano koro imiyo duongʼ sani kendo Nyasaye bende yudo duongʼ kuome.\wj* 
\v 32 \wj Ka Nyasaye oyudo duongʼ kuome, eka Wuowi bende biro yudo duongʼ kuome, kendo obiro miye duongʼ sani sani.\wj* 
\p  
\v 33 \wj “Nyithinda, pod abiro bedo kodu kuom thuolo matin. Bangʼe ubiro manya, to mana kaka ne anyiso jo-Yahudi e kaka anyisou sani, ni kama adhiye un ok unyal bire.\wj* 
\p  
\v 34 \wj “Amiyou chik manyien mawacho kama: Herreuru ngʼato gi ngʼato. Mana kaka aseherou e kaka nyaka uherru ngʼato gi ngʼato.\wj* 
\v 35 \wj Mano ema biro miyo ji duto ngʼeyo ni un jopuonjrena adier, ka uheroru ngʼato gi ngʼato.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 36 Simon Petro nopenje niya, “Ruoth, idhi kanye?” 
\p Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Kuma adhiye ok inyal luwae sani, to ibiro luwa kuno bangʼe.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 37 Petro nopenje niya, “Ruoth, angʼo momiyo ok anyal luwi sani? Aikora chiwo ngimana nikech in.” 
\p  
\v 38 Eka Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Bende inyalo chiwo ngimani nikech an adier? Anyisi ni kapok thuon gweno okok, wangʼ inikweda nyadidek!\wj* 
\c 14  
\s1 Yesu ojiwo jopuonjrene 
\p  
\v 1 \wj “Kik uwe chunyu chandre. Yieuru kuom Nyasaye, to An bende yieuru kuoma.\wj* 
\v 2 \wj E dala Wuora nitiere udi mangʼeny, kendo ka dine ok en kamano, to dikoro asenyisou. Adhi kuno mondo alosnu kar dak.\wj* 
\v 3 \wj To ka adhi mi alosonu kar dak, eka abiro duogo kawou mondo un bende ubed koda kama antiere.\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Ageno ni ungʼeyo yo madhi kuma adhiye.”\wj* 
\s1 Yesu e yo madhi ka Wuoro 
\p  
\v 5 Thoma nowachone niya, “Ruoth wakia kuma idhiye, koro ere kaka dwangʼe yo?” 
\p  
\v 6 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “An e yo kendo An e adiera bende An e ngima. Onge ngʼama nyalo biro ir Wuora ka ok okadho kuoma.\wj* 
\v 7 \wj Ka ungʼeya adier, to Wuora bende ubiro ngʼeyo. Chakre kawuononi ungʼeye kendo usenene.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 8 Filipo nowachone niya, “Ruoth, nyiswa Wuoro mondo kik wachak wachandi kendo.” 
\p  
\v 9 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Filipo, asebedo kodu kuom kinde mangʼeny, kare in pok ingʼeya? Ngʼato angʼata mosenena oseneno Wuoro, koro ere kaka ikelo wacho ni, ‘Nyiswa Wuoro’?\wj* 
\v 10 \wj Donge iyie ni An ei Wuora kendo Wuora ni e iya? Weche ma awachonu ok gin mana wechena awuon. Chutho, Wuora modak e iya ema timo tichne.\wj* 
\v 11 \wj Yie koda ka awacho ni an ei Wuora kendo Wuora ni e iya; to ka ok kamano, to yie kuom ranyisi gi honni ma asebedo ka atimo.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Awachonu adier, ni ngʼato ka ngʼato ma oyie kuoma biro timo gik ma asebedo ka atimo. Bende obiro timo gik madongo moloyo magi, nikech adhi ka Wuora.\wj* 
\v 13 \wj Abiro timo gimoro amora mukwayo e nyinga, eka Wuowi omi Wuoro duongʼ.\wj* 
\v 14 \wj Gimoro amora ma ukwayo e nyinga anatimnu.”\wj* 
\s1 Yesu osingo ni jopuonjrene Roho Maler 
\p  
\v 15 \wj “Ka uhera to ubiro timo gima achikou.\wj* 
\v 16 \wj Anakwa Wuoro, kendo obiro miyou Jakony machielo mondo obed kodu nyaka chiengʼ.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Jakonyno en Roho mar adier. Piny ok nyal rwake, nikech ok ginyal nene kendo gikiaye. Un to ungʼeye, nimar odak kodu kendo obiro bet eiu.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Ok abi weyou ka nyithi kiye; abiro biro iru.\wj* 
\v 19 \wj Odongʼ kinde matin to piny ok bi nena kendo. Un to pod ubiro nena, kendo ubiro bedo mangima nikech angima.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj Odiechiengʼno unungʼe ni an ei Wuora; kendo ni un e iya, kendo an eiu.\wj* 
\v 21 \wj Ngʼato angʼata mongʼeyo chikena kendo orito, e ngʼama ohera. Ngʼat mohera, Wuora biro hero, kendo an bende abiro here, mi afwenyrane.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 22 Eka Judas, ma ok Judas Iskariot, nowachone niya, “To Ruoth, angʼo momiyo wan ema idwaro fwenyorinwa to ok ni piny?” 
\p  
\v 23 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Ka ngʼato ohera to obiro rito puonjna, Wuora biro here, kendo wabiro biro ire mi walos kar dakwa kode.\wj* 
\v 24 \wj Ngʼama ok ohera ok nyal timo gima apuonjo. Weche muwinjogi ok gin maga awuon, to gin mag Wuora mane oora.\wj* 
\p  
\v 25 \wj “Gigi duto asenyisou kapod an kodu.\wj* 
\v 26 \wj To Jakony, ma en Roho Maler, ma Wuora biro oro e nyinga, biro puonjou weche duto, kendo obiro paronu gik moko duto ma asenyisou.\wj* 
\v 27 \wj Aweyonu kwe; kwe mara ema amiyou. En kwe ma pinyni ok nyal miyou. Kik chunyu parre kendo kik ubed maluor.\wj* 
\p  
\v 28 \wj “Ne uwinjo ka awacho niya, ‘Adhi to abiro duogo iru kendo.’ Ka dine bed ni uhera, to dine ubedo mamor ni adhi ka Wuora, nimar Wuora duongʼ moloya.\wj* 
\v 29 \wj Koro asenyisou kapok mano otimore, mondo ka gigo otimore to uyie.\wj* 
\v 30 \wj Ok abi wuoyo kodu amingʼa nimar ruodh pinyni biro, to oonge gi teko kuoma.\wj* 
\v 31 \wj Kata kamano, piny nyaka ngʼe ni ahero Wuora kendo ni atimo mana gima Wuora osechika mondo atim.\wj* 
\p \wj “Kuom mano, chunguru mondo wadhi.\wj* 
\c 15  
\s1 Yadh mzabibu kod bedene 
\p  
\v 1 \wj “An e mzabibu madier, kendo Wuora e japur mar mzabibuno.\wj* 
\v 2 \wj Bedena duto ma ok nyag olemo ongʼado oko, to bede duto manyago olemo olwero mondo omed nyak moloyo.\wj* 
\v 3 \wj Un usedoko maler nikech wach ma asewachonu.\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Sikuru kuoma, kaka an bende asiko kuomu, nikech onge bad yath manyalo nyago olemo kende owuon ka ok osiko e mzabibu. Un bende ok unyal nyago olemo ka ok usiko kuoma.\wj* 
\p  
\v 5 \wj “An e mzabibu, to un e bedene. Ka ngʼato osiko kuoma kendo an bende asiko kuome, to obiro nyago olemo mangʼeny, nimar onge gima unyalo timo ka upogoru koda.\wj* 
\v 6 \wj Ka ngʼato ok osiko kuoma, to ochalo gi bad yath motongʼ oko maner. Bede yath machal kamano ichoko kendo idiro e mach mi wangʼ.\wj* 
\v 7 \wj Ka usiko e iya kendo wechena osiko eiu, to unyalo kwayo gimoro amora ma chunyu gombo mi nomiu.\wj* 
\v 8 \wj Ka unyago olemo mangʼeny, to Wuora yudo duongʼ, kendo mano nyiso ni un jopuonjrena.\wj* 
\p  
\v 9 \wj “Mana kaka Wuoro osehera, e kaka an bende aseherou. Koro sikuru e herana.\wj* 
\v 10 \wj Ka urito chikena, to ubiro siko e herana, mana kaka an bende aserito chike Wuora kendo asiko e herane.\wj* 
\v 11 \wj Asenyisou wachni mondo morna obed eiu kendo mondo mor maru obed moromo chuth.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Chik ma amiyou ema: Herreuru ngʼato gi ngʼato, mana kaka an bende aseherou.\wj* 
\v 13 \wj Onge hera maduongʼ ma ngʼato nyalo herogo osiepene moloyo chiwonegi ngimane.\wj* 
\v 14 \wj Un osiepena mana kutimo gik ma achikou.\wj* 
\v 15 \wj Koro ok achak aluongu ni wasumbini nikech misumba ok ongʼeyo gima ruodhe timo; to aluongou ni osiepena nimar asenyisou gik moko duto mane apuonjora kuom Wuora.\wj* 
\v 16 \wj Un ne ok uyiera, an ema nayierou kendo aketou mondo udhi unyag olemo, ma en olemo masiko. Eka Wuora biro miyou gimoro amora mukwayo e nyinga.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Chik ma amiyou ema: Herreuru ngʼato gi ngʼato.\wj* 
\s1 Piny ochayo jopuonjre 
\p  
\v 18 \wj “Ka piny chayou, to ngʼeuru ni an ema ne gichaya mokwongo.\wj* 
\v 19 \wj Ka dine bed ni un mag pinyni, to piny dine oherou kaka joge owuon. Piny mon kodu nikech aseyierou, omiyo koro ok un mar pinyni.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj Paruru weche ma nawachonu ni, ‘Onge jatich maduongʼ moloyo ruodhe motiyone.’\wj*\f + \fr 15:20 \ft \xt Joh 13:16\f*\wj Omiyo ka an ema gisesanda, to un bende gibiro sandou. Ka gimako puonjna, to puonju bende gibiro mako.\wj* 
\v 21 \wj Gibiro timonu kamano nikech nyinga, nimar gikia Jal mane oora.\wj* 
\v 22 \wj Ka dine ok abiro mi awuoyo kodgi, to dine ok buch richo oloyogi. To koro, onge wach ma ginyalo umogo richogi.\wj* 
\v 23 \wj Ngʼama ochaya, ochayo Wuora bende.\wj* 
\v 24 \wj Ka dine bed ni ne pok atimo honni ma ngʼato angʼata pok otimo e diergi, to buch richo dine ok oloyogi, to sani koro giseneno honnigi duto, eka pod gichaya kaachiel gi Wuora bende.\wj* 
\v 25 \wj Mago duto osetimore mana mondo ochop gima ondiki e chikgi ni, ‘Ne gichaya kayiem nono.’\wj*\f + \fr 15:25 \ft \xt Zab 35:19; 69:4\f* 
\p  
\v 26 \wj “Ka Jakony ma abiro oronu koa ka Wuora, ma en Roho mar adier maa kuom Wuora nobi, enotim neno kuoma.\wj* 
\v 27 \wj To un bende nyaka utim nenda, nimar usebedo koda nyaka ne achak lando Injilini.\wj* 
\c 16  
\p  
\v 1 \wj “Asewachonu wechegi duto mondo kik ulal.\wj* 
\v 2 \wj Giniriembu e sinagogi; chutho ndalo biro ma ngʼama nonegu notim kamano kaparo ni otiyo ni Nyasaye.\wj* 
\v 3 \wj Ginitim kamano nikech ok gingʼeyo Wuora kata An.\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Asewachonu wechegi mondo ka ndalo ochopo to upar ni nasesiemou motelo. Ne ok awachonu wechegi chon nikech ne pod an kodu.\wj* 
\s1 Tich mar Roho Maler 
\p  
\v 5 \wj “Koro adhi ir Ngʼat mane oora, to onge ngʼato kuomu mapenja ni, ‘Idhi kanye?’\wj* 
\v 6 \wj Nikech gik ma asewachonu, omiyo un gi kuyo.\wj* 
\v 7 \wj To awachonu adier ni dhi ma adhigo biro kelonu ber. Ka ok adhi, to Jakony ok bi bironu; to ka adhi eka abiro oronugo.\wj* 
\v 8 \wj Ka obiro, nopuonj piny mondo ongʼe tiend richo, tim makare kod kum mabiro.\wj* 
\v 9 \wj Obiro nyisogi ni tamruok yie Kuoma en richo.\wj* 
\v 10 \wj Bende ka adok ir Wuora, kuma ok ginyal nenae, to giningʼe ni an ngʼat makare;\wj* 
\v 11 \wj kendo abiro nyisogi kuom kum mabiro, nikech ruodh pinyni koro bura oseloyo.\wj* 
\p  
\v 12 \wj “An gi weche mangʼeny monego awachnu, to ok unyal winjo tiendgi sani.\wj* 
\v 13 \wj To ka Roho mar adiera, osebiro, to enopuonju adiera duto. Ok enobed janeno kuome owuon, to nowachnu mana gik mosebedo kowinjo kendo obiro nyisou gik mabiro timore bangʼe.\wj* 
\v 14 \wj Enomiya duongʼ, nikech gik ma enowachnu nokaw kuoma.\wj* 
\v 15 \wj Gik moko duto ma Wuora nigo gin maga. Mano emomiyo ne awachonu ni gik moko duto ma Roho nowachnu nogol kuoma.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 16 Yesu nowacho bende niya, \wj “Odongʼ ndalo matin to ok ubi nena, to bangʼe matin achien ubiro nena kendo.”\wj* 
\s1 Kuyo mar jopuonjre biro lokore mor 
\p  
\v 17 Moko kuom jopuonjrene nopenjore e kindgi giwegi niya, “Ere tiend gima owachonwa ni, \wj ‘Bangʼ kinde matin ok ubi nena, to achien unuchak unena,’\wj* kendo owacho bende ni \wj ‘adhi ka Wuoro’\wj*?”  
\v 18 Negimedo penjore kendgi niya, “Ere gima oparo kowacho ni, \wj ‘Kinde matin\wj*?’ Ok wangʼeyo gima owacho.” 
\p  
\v 19 Yesu noneno ka gidwaro penje tiend wachno, omiyo nowachonegi niya, \wj “Dibed ni upenjoru e kindu tiend gima ne awachonu ni, ‘Odongʼ ndalo matin to ok ubi nena, to bangʼe matin achien ubiro nena?’\wj* 
\v 20 \wj Adier, adier awachonu, ni ubiro goyo nduru kendo ubiro ywak ka piny to winjo maber. Kuyo to ubiro kuyo, to kata kamano kuyo maru biro lokore mor achien.\wj* 
\v 21 \wj Dhako madwaro nywolo nyathi nyaka muoch kaa nikech sane ochopo; to bangʼ nywolo nyathine, wiye wil gi muoch, nikech omor ni osenywolo dhano mangima e piny.\wj* 
\v 22 \wj Kamano un bende sani en sau mar kuyo, to ubiro bedo mamor ka ananeu bangʼe, kendo onge ngʼama nomau mor maru.\wj* 
\v 23 \wj Chiengʼno ok unukwaya gimoro amora. Awachonu adier ni Wuora biro miyou gimoro amora mukwayo e nyinga.\wj* 
\v 24 \wj Nyaka sani pok ukwayo gimoro amora e nyinga. Kwauru to nomiu, eka nubed mamor chuth.\wj* 
\p  
\v 25 \wj “Kata obedo ni asebedo ka awuoyonu gi ngeche, to ndalo biro ma ok nawuo kodu kamano, to ananyisu maler kuom Wuora.\wj* 
\v 26 \wj Chiengʼno unukwa Wuoro e nyinga. Ok awach ni an ema nakwa Wuoro karu.\wj* 
\v 27 \wj Ooyo, Wuoro owuon oherou nikech usehera kendo useyie ni ne aa ka Nyasaye.\wj* 
\v 28 \wj Ne aa ka Wuoro mi adonjo e piny, to sani koro aweyo piny kendo adok ir Wuoro.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 29 Eka jopuonjre Yesu nowachone niya, “Ero koro iwuoyo kodwa maler ma ok itiyo gi ngeche.  
\v 30 Koro wayie ni ingʼeyo gik moko duto kendo ni onge tiende mondo ngʼato ochandi gi penjo mathoth. Mano omiyo wayie ni ne ia ka Nyasaye.” 
\p  
\v 31 Yesu nodwokogi niya, \wj “Kare ber ka koro uyie!\wj* 
\v 32 \wj To ndalo biro, kendo osechopo ma unukerue, ka ngʼato ka ngʼato kuomu ringo dok dalane. Unuweya mi adongʼ kenda, kata kamano ok an kenda, nimar Wuora ni koda.\wj* 
\p  
\v 33 \wj “Asenyisou gigi mondo uyud kwe moa kuoma. E pinyni ubiro neno chandruok, to beduru gi chir nikech aseloyo piny.”\wj* 
\c 17  
\s1 Yesu olamo 
\p  
\v 1 Kane Yesu osetieko wacho wechegi, nongʼiyo polo bangʼe olamo kama: 
\pm \wj “Wuora, sa osechopo. Mi Wuodi duongʼ mondo Wuodi bende omiyi duongʼ.\wj* 
\v 2 \wj Nimar isemiye loch ewi ji duto mondo omi ji duto misemiye oyud ngima mochwere.\wj* 
\v 3 \wj To ngima mochwere ema: ni mondo gingʼeyi in Nyasaye makende mar adier, kod Yesu Kristo, Jal miseoro.\wj* 
\v 4 \wj Asemiyi duongʼ e piny kuom tieko tich mane imiya mondo atim.\wj* 
\v 5 \wj To koro, Wuora, miya duongʼ e nyimi machal gi duongʼ mane an-go kodi kane piny pok obetie.\wj* 
\s1 Yesu olemo ne jopuonjrene 
\pm  
\v 6 \wj “Asehulo nyingi ni joma ne imiya e piny. Ne gin jogi, to ne imiyagi, kendo koro girito wachni.\wj* 
\v 7 \wj Koro gingʼeyo ni gik moko duto ma isemiya oa kuomi.\wj* 
\v 8 \wj Nimar ne amiyogi weche mane imiya kendo ne girwakogi. Gisengʼeyo gadier ni ne aa iri, kendo giseyie ni ne iora.\wj* 
\v 9 \wj Koro alamonegi. Ok alam ni piny, to alamo ni joma isemiya, nimar gin magi.\wj* 
\v 10 \wj Giga duto gin magi, kendo gigi duto gin maga, kendo aseyudo duongʼ kuomgi.\wj* 
\v 11 \wj Koro ndalona mag bet e piny orumo, nimar abiro iri, to gin pod gin e piny. Yaye Wuoro Maler, ritgi gi teko mar nyingi mane imiya, mondo gibed achiel mana kaka wan kodi wan achiel.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Kane pod an kodgi, to nachikogi kendo naritogi maber gi nying mane imiya. Onge kata achiel kuomgi moselal, makmana ngʼatno mane ochan ni nyaka lal mondo Ndiko ochop kare.\wj* 
\pm  
\v 13 \wj “Koro abiro iri, to awacho gigi kapod an e piny, mondo gibed gi morna mogundho eigi.\wj* 
\v 14 \wj Asemiyogi wachni, kendo piny ochayogi, nimar ok gin mag pinyni, mana kaka an bende ok an mar pinyni.\wj* 
\v 15 \wj Ok alam mondo igolgi oko e piny, to alamo ni iritgi mondo kik Ngʼama Rach timnegi marach.\wj* 
\v 16 \wj Ok gin mag pinyni, mana kaka an bende ok an mar pinyni.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Pwodhgi gi adierani, nikech Wachni en adiera.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Kaka ne iora e piny e kaka an bende aseorogi e piny.\wj* 
\v 19 \wj Apwodhora nikech gin, mondo omi gin bende gipwodhreni gi adiera.\wj* 
\s1 Yesu olemo ne joma oyie duto 
\pm  
\v 20 \wj “Ok alam ni gin kendgi, to alamo bende ni jogo mabiro yie kuoma bangʼ ka gisepuonjogi.\wj* 
\v 21 \wj Yaye Wuora, mi gibed achiel, mana kaka in e iya kendo an e iyi. Mad gin bende gibed e achiel kodwa, mondo piny oyie ni iseora.\wj* 
\v 22 \wj Asemiyogi duongʼ mane imiya, mondo gibed achiel kaka wan achiel,\wj* 
\v 23 \wj ka an kuomgi kendo in kuoma. Mad giriwre gibed gimoro achiel mondo piny ongʼe ni ne iora, kendo ni iseherogi mana kaka isehera.\wj* 
\pm  
\v 24 \wj “Wuora, adwaro ni joma isemiya obed koda kama antie, kendo ni gine duongʼna, ma en duongʼno misemiya nikech ne ihera kapok nochwe piny.\wj* 
\pm  
\v 25 \wj “Wuoro Makare, kata obedo ni piny ok ongʼeyi, an to angʼeyi, kendo jogi bende ongʼeyo ni ne iora.\wj* 
\v 26 \wj Asehulonegi nyingi, kendo pod abiro medo nyiso ji ngʼama in, mondo hera miherago obed kuomgi, kendo an awuon bende abed kuomgi.”\wj* 
\c 18  
\s1 Yesu omaki 
\p  
\v 1 Kane Yesu osetieko lemo, nowuok gi jopuonjrene, mine gingʼado holo mar Kidron. Loka mar holono ne nitie puodho moro mane nigi yiende mag Zeituni, kendo Yesu nodonjo kanyo kaachiel gi jopuonjrene. 
\p  
\v 2 To Judas, mane oyudo ondhoge, nongʼeyo kanyo, nikech Yesu ne thoro romo gi jopuonjrene kanyo.  
\v 3 Omiyo Judas nobiro e puodhono, kotelone migawo mar jolweny kod jotelo moko ma noa ir jodolo madongo gi jo-Farisai. Negitingʼo toje gi teyni kod gige lweny. 
\p  
\v 4 To kaka Yesu nongʼeyo gik moko duto mane biro timorene, nowuok oko mopenjogi niya, \wj “En ngʼa mudwaro?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 5 Negidwoko niya, “Wadwaro Yesu ma jo-Nazareth.” Yesu nowachonegi niya, 
\p \wj “An e en.”\wj* (To Judas mane ndhoge bende nochungʼ kodgi kanyo).  
\v 6 Kane Yesu owachonegi niya, \wj “An e En,”\wj* negigoyo okangʼ gidok chien mi gipodho piny. 
\p  
\v 7 Nochako openjogi niya, \wj “En ngʼa mudwaro?”\wj* 
\p Kendo neginwoyone niya, “Wadwaro Yesu ma jo-Nazareth.” 
\p  
\v 8 Yesu nodwokogi niya,\wj “Donge asenyisou ni An e En. Ka an ema umanya, to weuru jogi odhi mondi.”\wj* 
\v 9 Mano notimore mondo weche mane Yesu oyudo osewacho ochop kare. Nonyisogi niya, \wj “Onge kata ngʼato achiel moselal kuom joma ne imiya.”\wj*\f + \fr 18:9 \ft \xt Joh 6:39\f* 
\p  
\v 10 Eka Simon Petro, mane oyudo nigi ligangla, nowuodho liganglane kendo notongʼo jatij jadolo maduongʼ mi ochodo ite ma korachwich, kendo nying jatijno ne en Malko. 
\p  
\v 11 Yesu nokwero Petro kowachone niya, \wj “Dwok liganglani e olalo! Idwaro mona metho e okombe ma Wuora osemiya nangʼo?”\wj* 
\s1 Oter Yesu ir Anas jadolo 
\p  
\v 12 Eka migawo mar jolweny gi jatendgi kod jotend jo-Yahudi nomako Yesu. Ne gitweye  
\v 13 mi gitere ir Anas. Anas ne en jadolo maduongʼ e higano bende ne en jaduongʼ Kaifas.  
\v 14 Kaifas e ngʼama noyudo osengʼado rieko ni jo-Yahudi ni ber mondo ngʼato achiel otho ni ji duto. 
\s1 Petro okwedo Yesu mokwongo 
\p  
\v 15 Simon Petro gi japuonjre machielo noluwo bangʼ Yesu. To nikech japuonjre machielono ne jadolo maduongʼ ongʼeyo, nodonjo gi Yesu nyaka ei laru mar jadolo maduongʼ,  
\v 16 to Petro to nodongʼ karito e dhoot oko. Japuonjre machielo ma jadolo maduongʼ nongʼeyono noduogo mowuoyo gi nyako mane rito welo madonjo mi nokawo Petro gidonjogo iye. 
\p  
\v 17 Nyako mane ni e dhootno nopenjo Petro niya, “Donge in bende in achiel kuom jopuonjre ngʼatni, koso ariambo?” 
\p Nodwoke niya, “Ooyo, ok an.” 
\p  
\v 18 To nikech piny ne ngʼich, jotich gi jotelo nochungʼ kolworo mach manoyudo gisemoko mondo gio. Petro bende nochungʼ kodgi kanyo kaoyo mach. 
\s1 Jadolo maduongʼ oyalo Yesu 
\p  
\v 19 E thuolono jadolo maduongʼ nomiyo Yesu penjo kuom wach jopuonjrene kod puonjne. 
\p  
\v 20 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Asebedo ka awuoyo e lela ni oganda, kendo asebedo ka apuonjo ei sinagoke gi hekalu, kuonde ma jo-Yahudi duto chokoree. Onge gimoro amora masewacho lingʼ-lingʼ.\wj* 
\v 21 \wj En angʼo momiyo umiya penjo? Penjuru joma osebedo ka winja. Gin gingʼeyo maber gima nawacho.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 22 Kane Yesu owacho kamano, achiel kuom askeche mane ochungʼ bute nothalo lembe kawacho niya, “Kamano e kaka inyalo dwoko jadolo maduongʼ adier?” 
\p  
\v 23 To Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Kapo ni awachone gimoro amora marach to hul ane gino. To kapo nawacho adier to ithala nangʼo?”\wj* 
\v 24 Eka Anas nochiwo Yesu mondo oter ir Kaifas, jadolo maduongʼ, ka pod otweye. 
\s1 Petro okwedo Yesu kendo 
\p  
\v 25 Kane oyudo Simon Petro pod ochungʼ oyo mach, negipenje niya, “Idagi ni ok in achiel kuom jopuonjrene, koso iyie?” 
\p Nodagi kowacho niya, “Ooyo, ok an.” 
\p  
\v 26 Achiel kuom jotich jadolo maduongʼ mane en wat ngʼat mane Petro ongʼado ite cha, nochome tir, kapenje niya, “Donge nende aneni kode e puoth Zeituni?”  
\v 27 To Petro nochako okwer kendo, kendo gikanyono thuon gweno nochako kok. 
\s1 Yesu oter e nyim Pilato 
\p  
\v 28 Eka jo-Yahudi nokawo Yesu koa ir Kaifas motere nyaka e od ruoth Pilato. Sechego koro piny nosechako yawore, omiyo jo-Yahudi ne ok odonjo ei dala ruoth, mondo kik gibed mogak. Negidwaro ni gicham Pasaka ka giler.  
\v 29 Omiyo Pilato nowuoknigi oko mopenjogi niya, “Ngʼatni udonjone gi ketho mage?” 
\p  
\v 30 Negidwoke niya, “Ka dine bed ni ok en jaketho, to dine ok wakele e nyimi ka.” 
\p  
\v 31 Pilato nowachonegi niya, “Kaweuru un uwegi udhi ungʼadne bura kaka chiku dwaro.” 
\p To jo-Yahudi nodagi, kagiwacho niya, “Wan waonge gi teko mar ngʼado ne ngʼato buch tho.”  
\v 32 Mano notimore mondo weche Yesu mane oyudo osewacho kuom tho mane obiro thogo ochop kare. 
\p  
\v 33 Eka Pilato nodok e ode, kendo noluongo Yesu ire mopenje niya, “In e ruodh jo-Yahudi?” 
\p  
\v 34 Yesu nopenje niya, \wj “Gima ipenjano oa e pachi iwuon koso jomoko nono ema owachonigo kuoma?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 35 Pilato nodwoke niya, “Iparo ni an bende an ja-Yahudi? Jou owuon gi jodolou madongo ema oketi e lweta. Nyisa, en angʼo misetimo?” 
\p  
\v 36 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Pinyruodha ok en mar pinyni. Ka dine bed ni en, to jotichna dine ogore mi gitamo jo-Yahudi maka. To koroni, pinyruodha aa kamachielo.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 37 Pilato nowacho niya, “Kare in ruoth?” 
\p Yesu nodwoko niya, \wj “In kare kuom wacho ni an ruoth. Chutho mano emomiyo nonywola, kendo mano emomiyo ne abiro e pinyni, mondo atim neno kuom adiera. Ngʼato ka ngʼato ma jakora adiera winja.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 38 Pilato nopenje niya, “Adiera en angʼo?” Bangʼ penjo kamano to nochako odok oko ir jo-Yahudi, mi owachonegi niya, “Ok ayudo ketho kata achiel kuom ngʼatni minyalo ngʼadnego bura.  
\v 39 To kaka en kitu mondo agonynu achiel kuom joma otwe e kinde mag sawo mar Pasaka, duher mondo agonynu ‘ruodh jo-Yahudi’ koso?” 
\p  
\v 40 To ne gikokne matek, kagiwacho riat niya, “Ooyo, ok en! Barabas ema imiwa!” Barabas ne en jamecho. 
\c 19  
\s1 Ongʼadne Yesu buch tho 
\p  
\v 1 Eka Pilato nokawo Yesu mi ochiwe mondo ochwade.  
\v 2 Jolweny nokado osimbo mar kudho, mi gisidhone kendo negiketo e wiye. Ne girwakone kandho makwar,  
\v 3 kendo negisiko ka gidhi ire sa ka sa kagiwachone niya, “Ruodh jo-Yahudi, mondo omi duongʼ!” Negisiko ka githalo lembe. 
\p  
\v 4 Pilato nochako owuok oko kendo mowacho ni jo-Yahudi niya, “Neuru, eri akele e nyimu mondo ungʼe ni ok ayudo ketho kata achiel kuome minyalo ngʼadnego bura.”  
\v 5 Kane Yesu owuok oko korwako osimbo mar kudho gi kandho makwar, Pilato nowachonegi niya, “Eri ngʼatno!” 
\p  
\v 6 E sa ma jodolo madongo gi jotendgi nonene, negigoyo koko matek niya, “Gure! Gure!” 
\p To Pilato nowachonegi niya, “Kaweuru un uwegi udhi ugure. An ok ayudo ketho moro amora kuome minyalo ngʼadonego bura.” 
\p  
\v 7 To jo-Yahudi nokone koramo niya, “Wan gi chik, kendo kaluwore gi chikwano, nyaka otho, nikech noketore ni en Wuod Nyasaye.” 
\p  
\v 8 Kane Pilato owinjo mano, luoro nomedo make moloyo,  
\v 9 omiyo nochako odok e ode, mopenjo Yesu niya, “In jakanye?” To Yesu ne ok odwoke.  
\v 10 Pilato nowachone niya, “Idagi wuoyo koda nangʼo? Bende ingʼeyo ni an gi teko ma anyalo gonyigo kata gurigo?” 
\p  
\v 11 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Ok dibedo gi teko moro amora kuoma ka dine bed ni ok omiyigo koa malo. Kuom mano ngʼama noketa e lweti nigi ketho maduongʼ moloyo richo misetimo.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 12 Kochakore e sechego, Pilato notemo gonyo Yesu, kata kamano jo-Yahudi nomedo kok matek kagiwacho niya, “Kiweyo ngʼatni thuolo modhi, to ok in osiep Kaisar. Ngʼato ka ngʼato ma ketore ni en ruoth, kedo gi Kaisar.” 
\p  
\v 13 Kane Pilato owinjo mano, nogolo Yesu oko kendo nobet piny e kome mar ngʼado bura kama iluongo ni Laru motingʼore malo mar kidi (miluongo gi dho jo-Hibrania ni Gabatha).  
\v 14 Ne en chiengʼ ikruok mar jumb Pasaka, kar sa auchiel. 
\p Pilato nowachone jo-Yahudi niya, “Ma e Ruodhu!” 
\p  
\v 15 To ne gikok niya, “Gole e wangʼwa! Gole e wangʼwa! Gure!” 
\p Pilato nopenjogi niya, “Udwaro ni agur ruodhu?” 
\p Jodolo madongo nodwoke niya, “Wan waonge gi ruoth machielo makmana Kaisar kende.” 
\p  
\v 16 Eka Pilato nokete e lwetgi mondo gigure, 
\s1 Ogur Yesu 
\p kendo jolweny nokawo Yesu modhigo.  
\v 17 Yesu nowuok kanyo kotingʼo msalape owuon nyaka kar Hanga Wich (miluongo gi dho jo-Hibrania ni Golgotha).  
\v 18 Negigure kanyo, kaachiel gi ji ariyo mamoko. Yesu ne ogur e diere, ka ngʼato achiel ni e bathe konchiel to moro e bathe komachielo. 
\p  
\v 19 Pilato ne nigi milome moro ma nondiko bangʼe oguro ewi msalaba gimalo. Nondike niya: 
\pc Ma en Yesu Ja-Nazareth, Ruodh Jo-Yahudi. 
\m  
\v 20 Jo-Yahudi mangʼeny nosomo ndikono, nimar kama nogure Yesu ne ni machiegni gi dala maduongʼ, kendo milomeno nondiki e dho jo-Hibrania, gi Latin kod dho jo-Yunani.  
\v 21 To jodolo madongo mag jo-Yahudi nokwedo gima ne Pilato ondikono kagiwacho niya, “We ndiko ni ‘Ruodh jo-Yahudi,’ ndik ni, ngʼatni noketore ni en ruodh jo-Yahudi.” 
\p  
\v 22 Pilato nowacho niya, “Gima asendiko, asendiko.” 
\p  
\v 23 Kane jolweny oseguro Yesu, negikawo lepe mi gipogogi nyadingʼwen, bangʼe gipogore moro ka moro, kargi ji angʼwen. Lawe mar kandho kende ema ne giweyo. En ne oonge gi wangʼ usi, to notwangʼe machalre, chakre malo nyaka piny. 
\p  
\v 24 Negiwacho e kindgi giwegi niya, “En kik wayieche. Wagouru ombulu e dierwa mondo wangʼe ngʼama kawe.”\f + \fr 19:24 \ft \xt Zab 22:18\f* 
\p Mano notimore mondo Ndiko ochop kare manowacho niya, 
\q1 “Ne gipogore lepa e kindgi giwegi 
\q2 kendo gigoyo ombulu ne nangana.” 
\m Mano e kaka ne jolwenygo notimo. 
\p  
\v 25 Min Yesu gi nyamin min-gi, gi Maria ma chi Kiliopa kod Maria ma aa Magdala nochungʼ but msalaba.  
\v 26 Kane Yesu oneno min-gi gi japuonjre ma nohero kochungʼ machiegni kanyo, nowachone min-gi niya, \wj “Mama, neye wuodi!”\wj* 
\v 27 Nowacho bende ni japuonjreno niya, \wj “Neye mamau!”\wj* Chakre chiengʼno japuonjreno nokawe odhi kode dalane owuon. 
\s1 Tho mar Yesu 
\p  
\v 28 Bangʼ, kane koro osengʼeyo ni gik moko duto osetimore kaka dwarore, mondo Ndiko ochop kare, Yesu nowacho niya, \wj “Riyo oloya.”\wj* 
\v 29 To ne nitie njagi motingʼo kongʼo makech kanyo, omiyo ne giluto siponj e iye bangʼe ne gichwoyo siponjno ewi kede moro mi gitere nyaka e dho Yesu.  
\v 30 Kane Yesu osebilo kongʼono nowacho niya, \wj “Duto koro orumo.”\wj* Eka nokulo wiye piny, kendo chunye nochot. 
\p  
\v 31 Ne en odiechiengʼ motelo ne odiechieng Pasaka. Nikech jo-Yahudi ne ok dwar mondo owe ringre Yesu koliero e msalaba chiengʼ Sabato, ne gikwayo Pilato mondo one ni otur tiende joma nogur, kendo olor ringregi.  
\v 32 Omiyo jolweny nobiro moturo tiend ngʼat mokwongo ma nogur gi Yesu, kod tiende ngʼat machielo bende.  
\v 33 Kane gibiro ir Yesu mi giyudo nine osetho, ne ok gituro tiendene.  
\v 34 Kar timo kamano, to achiel kuom askechego nochwowo ngʼet Yesu gi tongʼ, mi remo gi pi nochwer.  
\v 35 Ngʼama noneno ka gigo timore ema ochiwo nenoni kendo nende en adier. Ongʼeyo ni owacho adiera, kendo ohulo wechegi mondo un bende uyie.  
\v 36 Gigi notimore mondo Ndiko ochop kare kaka nondiki niya, “Onge kata choke achiel ma notur.”\f + \fr 19:36 \ft \xt Wuo 12:46; Kwa 9:12; Zab 34:20\f* 
\v 37 Ndiko machielo bende wacho niya, “Giniket geno margi kuom Jal mane gichwowo gi tongʼ.”\f + \fr 19:37 \ft \xt Zek 12:10\f* 
\s1 Yik mar Yesu 
\p  
\v 38 Bangʼe Josef ja-Arimathaya nokwayo Pilato mondo omiye ringre Yesu. Josef ne en japuonjre Yesu to nobedo kamano lingʼ-lingʼ nikech noluoro jo-Yahudi. Kane Pilato osemiye thuolo, nobiro mokawo ringre Yesu.  
\v 39 Nikodemo mane oseyudo odhi ir Yesu gotieno chiengʼ moro nodhi gi Josef. Nikodemo nokelo yien moko mangʼwe ngʼar moru kaachiel mane-mane madirom kilo piero adek gangʼwen.  
\v 40 Negikawo ringre Yesu mi giwiro gi modhigo bangʼe giboye gi lewni marep-rep molir olir, kaka chik jo-Yahudi mar yiko ngʼato dwaro.  
\v 41 To kama negigure Yesuno ne nitie puodho moro, kendo ei puodhono ne nitie bur manyien mapok oike ngʼato.  
\v 42 Nikech ne en odiechieng jo-Yahudi mar ikruok ne Sabato, kendo nikech bur mar ik ne ni machiegni, negiiko Yesu kanyo. 
\c 20  
\s1 Chier mar Yesu 
\p  
\v 1 To odiechiengʼ mokwongo mar juma, kogwen, kane piny pod olil, Maria ma aa Magdala nodhi e liel, mi noneno ka kidi osengʼiel oko e dho lielno.  
\v 2 Omiyo noringo modhi ir Simon Petro kod japuonjre machielo mane Yesu ohero, kendo nowachonegi niya, “Gisekawo ringre Ruoth gigolo e liel kama noyike, kendo koro wakia kama giketee!” 
\p  
\v 3 Kuom mano, Petro gi japuonjre machielono nowuok modhi kama noyike.  
\v 4 Negiringo giduto, to japuonjre machielono noyombo Petro, mi nokuongone chopo e liel.  
\v 5 Nokulore mongʼicho, kendo noneno lewni mayom molir olir kod law ik ma nonalgo wi Yesu kani ei bur kanyo. To kata kamano, ne ok odonjo e iye.  
\v 6 Eka Simon Petro, mane ringo bangʼe bende notundo. En to nodonjo nyaka ei bur ik, mi noneno lewni mayom molir olir ka ni kanyo,  
\v 7 kaachiel gi law ik mane onalgo wi Yesu. Nangano noban maber, kendo ne en kar kende, mopogore gi kama lewni mayom molir olir ne nitie.  
\v 8 Mogik, japuonjre machielo, mane okwongo chopo e bur yikno, bende nodonjo ei bur mi noneno kendo noyie.  
\v 9 (Nyaka ae thuolono ne pok gingʼeyo, koa e Ndiko, ni nochuno ni Yesu nyaka ne chier mi aa kuom joma otho.)  
\v 10 Eka jopuonjre nodok e miechgi. 
\s1 Yesu ofwenyorene Maria ma aa Magdala 
\p  
\v 11 Maria nochungʼ oko e dho bur kaywak. Kane oyudo oywak, nokulore mongʼiyo i bur,  
\v 12 kendo noneno malaike ariyo morwako lewni marochere, kobet piny kama ringre Yesu nopielie, ka moro ni yo ka wiye, to machielo ni yo ka tiende. 
\p  
\v 13 Negipenje niya, “Nyarwa, iywago angʼo?” 
\p Nowachonegi niya, “Gisekawo Ruodha gidhigo, to akia kama giketee.”  
\v 14 Bangʼ wacho kamano, nolokore ongʼiyo ngʼeye, kendo noneno Yesu kochungʼ kanyo, to ne ok ongʼeyo ni en Yesu. 
\p  
\v 15 Yesu nopenje niya, \wj “Nyarwa, iywago angʼo? En ngʼa mimanyo?”\wj* 
\p En to noparo ni mano jarit puodho ema wuoyo kode, omiyo nopenje niya, “Jaduongʼ, ka dipo ni in ema ne ikawe idhi kode, to nyisa kama iseketee, mondo adhi akawe.” 
\p  
\v 16 Yesu noluonge niya, \wj “Maria!”\wj* 
\p Nolokore mi ongʼiye koluonge matek gi dho jo-Hibrania niya, \tl “Raboni!”\tl* (tiende ni “Japuonj”). 
\p  
\v 17 Yesu nowachone niya, \wj “Kik itweri kuoma, nimar pok adok ka Wuora, to dhi ir owetena mondo inyisgi ni, ‘Adok ir Wuora ma en Wuoru un bende, kendo Nyasacha ma en Nyasachu.’ ”\wj* 
\p  
\v 18 Maria nyar Magdala nodhi ir jopuonjre monyisogi Injili niya, “Aseneno Ruoth!” Kendo Ruoth ema osenyisa weche ma awachonugi. 
\s1 Yesu ofwenyore ne jopuonjrene 
\p  
\v 19 Godhiambo mar odiechiengʼ mokwongo mar juma, jopuonjre nochokore kanyakla, kendo ne giloro dhoudi nikech negiluoro jo-Yahudi, Yesu nobiro mochungʼ e diergi kendo nowachonegi niya, \wj “Kwe obed kodu!”\wj* 
\v 20 Bangʼ kane osewacho ma, nonyisogi lwetene gi ngʼetne. Jopuonjre ne mor mokalo kane gineno Ruoth. 
\p  
\v 21 Yesu nochako owachonegi kendo niya, \wj “Beduru gi kwe! Mana kaka Wuora oseora e kaka an bende aorou.”\wj* 
\v 22 Bangʼ wachonegi wechego, nokudho muche kuomgi, kowachonegi niya, \wj “Nwangʼuru Roho Maler.\wj* 
\v 23 \wj Ngʼato angʼata muweyone richone nowenegi, to ka ok uweyonegi, to ok nowenegi.”\wj* 
\s1 Yesu ofwenyore ne Thoma 
\p  
\v 24 Thoma (ma bende iluongo ni Didimas), ma en achiel kuom jopuonjre apar gariyo, ne ok ni kodgi e kinde mane Yesu ofwenyorenigi.  
\v 25 Omiyo jopuonjre mamoko nokone niya, “Waseneno Ruoth!” 
\p To nowachonegi niya, “An to ka ok aneno lwete kuonde mane musmal ochwowo, mi aketo lith lweta kuondego, kendo asoyo lweta e ngʼetne, to ok abi yie wachno.” 
\p  
\v 26 Bangʼ juma achiel, jopuonjre ne ni ei ot kendo, to chiengʼno Thoma ne ni kodgi. Kata obedo ni dhoudi nolor, Yesu nobiro mochungʼ e diergi momosogi niya, \wj “Okweuru!”\wj* 
\v 27 Eka nowachone Thoma niya, \wj “Ket lith lweti kae kendo nee lwetena. Chor lweti kuoma bangʼe iketi e ngʼetna. We bedo ngʼama riwo gi kiawa, bed ngʼama nigi yie!”\wj* 
\p  
\v 28 Thoma nodwoke niya, “Ruodha kendo Nyasacha!” 
\p  
\v 29 Eka Yesu nowachone niya, \wj “In iyie nikech isenena, to ogwedh joma pok onena, to oseyie.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 30 Yesu notimo ranyisi gi honni mamoko mangʼeny, ka jopuonjrene neno, ma ok ondiki e kitabuni.  
\v 31 To magi ondiki mondo uyie ni Yesu e Kristo ma Wuod Nyasaye, kendo mondo ka uyie kamano, to ubed gi ngima e nyinge. 
\c 21  
\s1 Yesu omiyo jopuonjrene omako rech mangʼeny 
\p  
\v 1 Bangʼ ka gigo nosetimore, Yesu nochako onenore kendo ni jopuonjrene e dho Nam Tiberia. To nenruokne kodgi nobet kama:  
\v 2 Simon Petro, Thoma (ma bende iluongo ni Didimas), Nathaniel mane aa Kana e piny Galili, yawuot Zebedi, kod jopuonjre mamoko ariyo, noyudo ochokore kanyakla.  
\v 3 Simon Petro nowachonegi niya, “Adok lupo” kendo negiwachone niya, “Wan bende wadok kodi.” Omiyo negiwuok gidhi kendo negidonjo ei yie. To otienono duto onge gima negimako. 
\p  
\v 4 Kinyne kogwen, Yesu nochungʼ e dho nam, to jopuonjre ne ok ongʼeye. 
\p  
\v 5 Noluongogi niya, \wj “Jowadwa, bende unie gi rech moro?”\wj* 
\p Negidwoke niya, “Ooyo.” 
\p  
\v 6 Nowachonegi niya, \wj “Boluru gogo mau yo bat korachwich mar yie, to ubiro mako rech.”\wj* Kane gitimo kamano, ywayo gogo nyaka ei yie notamogi, nikech rech ne ngʼeny mohewogi ywayo. 
\p  
\v 7 Eka japuonjre ma Yesu nohero nowacho ni Petro niya, “En Ruoth!” Sa nogono ma Simon Petro nowinje kowacho niya, “En Ruoth,” notweyo lawe mar abola e nungone, nimar noyudo osegole oko mi nochikore ei pi.  
\v 8 Jopuonjre mamoko to ne luwo bangʼe ka gin ei yie, kendo ka giywayo gogo ma rech opongʼo, nimar ne koro ok gin mabor gi dho nam, kendo nodongʼnegi mana fut mia ariyo gi piero ochiko gabich kende to gichop oko.  
\v 9 Kane gigowo e dho nam, negineno mach maliel ka ni kanyo ka oket rech e wiye, kod makati moko. 
\p  
\v 10 Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “Keluru rech moko kuom mago ma usemako.”\wj* 
\v 11 Simon Petro nodonjo ei pi, mi noywayo gogo nyaka dho wath. Nopongʼ gi rech madongo dongo ma dirom rech mia achiel gi piero abich gadek, to kata negingʼeny kamano, to gogo ne ok oyiech.  
\v 12 Yesu nowachonegi niya, \wj “Suduru machiegni uchiem.”\wj* Onge japuonjre kata achiel mane ohedhore penje niya, “In ngʼa?” Negingʼeyo ni en Ruoth.  
\v 13 Yesu nobiro mokawo makati omiyogi, kendo rech bende nomiyogi kamano.  
\v 14 Mano ne en fwenyruok mar Yesu mar adek ni jopuonjrene bangʼ chier aa kuom joma otho. 
\s1 Yesu odwogo Petro e tich 
\p  
\v 15 Kane gisetieko chiemo, Yesu nopenjo Simon Petro niya, \wj “Simon wuod Johana, bende ihera adier moloyo jogi?”\wj* 
\p Nodwoke niya, “Ee, Ruoth, ingʼeyo ni aheri.” 
\p Yesu nowachone niya, \wj “Kare pidh nyiromba.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 16 Nochako openje kendo mar ariyo niya, \wj “Simon wuod Johana, bende ihera adier?”\wj* 
\p Nodwoke niya, “Ee, Ruoth, ingʼeyo ni aheri.” 
\p Yesu nowachone niya, \wj “Kare rit romba.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 17 Nopenje mar adek niya, \wj “Simon wuod Johana, bende ihera?”\wj* 
\p Petro nokuyo nikech Yesu nopenje mar adek niya, \wj “Bende ihera?”\wj* Nodwoke niya, “Ruoth, in ingʼeyo gik moko duto; ingʼeyo ni aheri.” 
\p Yesu nowachone niya, \wj “Kare pidh romba.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj Adier, adier awachoni, kane pod itin, to nirwakori kendi kendo ne inyalo dhi kamoro amora mihero; to kibiro doko moti, to ibiro rieyo bedeni ne ngʼama chielo ma biro rwakoni lepi mi teri kuma ok idwar dhiye.”\wj* 
\v 19 Yesu nowacho mano mondo onyisgo kit tho ma Petro ne biro miyogo Nyasaye duongʼ. Eka nowachone niya, \wj “Luwa!”\wj* 
\p  
\v 20 Petro nolokore moneno japuonjre mane Yesu ohero kaluwogi. (Ma e ngʼat mane otenore kuom Yesu kane gilworo mesa gichamo chiemb odhiambo, mi openje niya, “Ruoth, en ngʼa madwaro ndhogi?”)  
\v 21 Kane Petro onene, nopenjo niya, “Ruoth, to en to?” 
\p  
\v 22 Yesu nodwoke niya, \wj “Ka adwaro ni osik kongima nyaka aduogi, to mano chandi nangʼo? In to luwa!”\wj* 
\v 23 Dwoko mane Yesu odwokono nomiyo wachno olandore e kind jowete ni japuonjreno ok bi tho ngangʼ, to Yesu to nowacho mana niya, \wj “Ka adwaro ni osik kongima nyaka aduogi, to mano chandi nangʼo?”\wj* 
\p  
\v 24 Ma e japuonjre makoro timo neno kuom gigi kendo en bende ema nondikogi piny. Wangʼeyo ni nende en adier. 
\p  
\v 25 Yesu notimo gik mangʼeny mamoko. Ka dine ndikgi duto moro ka moro kuomgi, to an gi ratiro ni kata mana piny ngima ok doromo kano kitepe duto ma dine ondiki.